20solving%20but%20India%20certainly%20is%20trusted%20by%20Israel%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20problem%20seeing%20them%20involved%20in%20our%20issues.%20We%20trust%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ambassador%20said%20around%201%2C000%20Indians%20have%20been%20evacuated%20from%20Israel%20and%2020%2C000%20are%20still%20there%2C%20asserting%20that%20most%20of%20them%20did%20not%20want%20to%20leave%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarian%20Aspects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20to%20him%20that%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20set%20to%20visit%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20he%20was%20asked%20whether%20there%20could%20be%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20to%20the%20crisis%2C%20Mr%20Gilon%20said%20he%20did%20not%20think%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20humanitarian%20aspect%20of%20the%20war%2C%20like%20releasing%20Israeli%20hostages%20that%20were%20kidnapped%20could%20be%20a%20solution.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Hamas%2C%20ISIS%2C%20terror%20organisations%2C%20there%20is%20no%20solution%20with%20them.%20The%20only%20solution%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20cannot%20execute%20horrific%2C%20barbaric%20attacks%20like%20they%20did%20last%20Saturday%20is%20to%20go%20after%20them%20and%20kill%20them.%20We%20don't%20see%20any%20other%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20aid%20being%20allowed%20into%20Gaza%2C%20Mr%20Gilon%20said%20negotiations%20were%20on%20as%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20humanitarian%20aspect%20of%20the%20conflict.%20He%20claimed%20people%20are%20speaking%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20issues%20in%20Gaza%20but%20not%20about%20the%20200%20families%20from%20Israel%20whose%20relatives%20are%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20has%20warned%20of%20a%20real%20catastrophe%20with%20just%2024%20hours%20of%20water%2C%20electricity%20and%20fuel%20left.%20When%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20this%2C%20Mr%20Gilon%20said%20people%20are%20missing%20the%20context%20and%20forgetting%20what%20happened%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%201%2C400%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack.%20He%20said%20water%20supply%20has%20been%20restored%20and%20claimed%20that%20Israel%20cares%20more%20about%20the%20Gazans%20than%20Hamas%20and%20warned%20them%20to%20evacuate%20from%20the%20north%2C%20while%20Hamas%20was%20stopping%20them%20and%20using%20them%20as%20human%20shields.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Can%20Fight%20On%20Multiple%20Fronts'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20war%20expanding%20and%20seeing%20the%20involvement%20of%20more%20countries%2C%20Mr%20Gilon%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Arab%20nations%2C%20the%20moderate%20countries%2C%20know%20that%20jihadist%20Islamist%20extremism%20is%20a%20risk%20to%20them%20as%20much%20-%20or%20more%20-%20as%20it%20is%20a%20risk%20to%20us.%20The%20issue%20is%20not%20Arab%20states%2C%20it%20is%20a%20non-Arab%20state%20called%20Iran.%20It%20is%20very%20much%20connected%20to%20everything%20that%20happened...%20We%20know%20that%20Iran%20has%20been%20training%2C%20arming%20and%20financing%20Hamas%20for%20years.%20Just%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20Iranian%20foreign%20minister%20went%20to%20Beirut%20and%20met%20with%20Hezbollah%2C%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20representatives%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHezbollah%2C%20which%20is%20the%20de%20facto%20ruler%20and%20wing%20of%20Iran%20in%20Lebanon%20has%20been%20threatening%20to%20open%20another%20frontier%20in%20the%20northern%20border%20and%20started%20shooting%20and%20also%20killing%20some%20Israelis%20on%20our%20side.%20We%20prefer%20not%20to%20have%20another%20front%2C%20but%20we%20say%20very%20clearly%20that%20if%20Hezbollah%2C%20Iran%20decide%20to%20open%20another%20front%2C%20Israel%20is%20able%20to%20fight%20on%20multiple%20fronts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gilon%20said%20Hezbollah%20is%20not%20the%20master%20of%20its%20own%20will%20and%20has%20Iran%20behind%20it%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20even%20closer%20to%20Iran%20than%20Hamas%20is.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Shiite%20and%20Hamas%20are%20Sunnis.%20(Hassan)%20Nasrallah%2C%20their%20leader%2C%20has%20said%20more%20than%20once%20that%20he%20is%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20army%20of%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerailing%20Key%20Initiatives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20attacks%20would%20not%20set%20the%20clock%20back%20on%20the%20normalisation%20of%20Arab-Israel%20ties%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20something%20Iran%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel%20would%20want.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Middle%20East%20was%20changed%20by%20the%20Abraham%20Accords.%20Now%20Saudi%20Arabia%20was%20getting%20close.%20The%20economic%20initiative%20I2U2%2C%20which%20includes%20India%2C%20was%20also%20part%20of%20it.%20Now%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20creating%20a%20route%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20into%20Israel%20and%20the%20Mediterranean.%20I%20think%20they%20wanted%20to%20derail%20all%20of%20that%2C%20that%20was%20their%20aim.%20But%2C%20from%20a%20logical%20point%20of%20view%2C%20these%20extremists%20like%20Hamas%20and%20ISIS%20are%20the%20enemies%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697539740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjc41899_israeli-ambassador-naor-gilon-650_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-trusts-india-it-has-a-lot-of-credibility-israeli-envoy-to-ndtv-4488985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20trusts%20India%2C%20and%20the%20country's%20quick%20condemnation%20of%20the%20Hamas%20te