ment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpoland-election-tusks-opposition-alliance-secures-majority%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Louis%20Vuitton%2C%20And%20A%20Bagful%20Of%20Questions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20last%20year's%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20opposition%20members%20were%20trying%20to%20corner%20the%20Modi%20government%20during%20a%20debate%20on%20rising%20prices.%20The%20thrust%20of%20their%20argument%20was%20that%20circumstances%20had%20made%20survival%20difficult%20for%20a%20common%20citizen%20as%20the%20household%20budget%20had%20gone%20awry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20rose%20to%20speak%2C%20the%20Sansad%20TV%20camera%20focused%20on%20her.%20Seated%20next%20to%20her%20was%20her%20party%20colleague%20Mahua%20Moitra.%20Moitra%20perhaps%20realised%20that%20the%20live%20broadcast%20on%20the%20sensitive%20topic%20was%20also%20catching%20her%20super%20expensive%20Louis%20Vuitton%20handbag.%20The%20next%20second%2C%20she%20was%20seen%20shifting%20the%20bag%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20away%20from%20the%20camera.%20That%20clip%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bag%20cost%20Rs%201.60%20lakh.%20These%20are%20personal%20choices%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20one%20can%20afford.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20a%20Member%20of%20parliament.%20Moitra's%20profile%20says%20she%20has%20been%20an%20investment%20banker%2C%20so%20it%20was%20naturally%20assumed%20that%20she%20had%20that%20kind%20of%20purchasing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20her%202019%20debut%20in%20parliament%20with%20a%20viral%20speech%20targeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%2C%20Moitra%20had%20been%20kept%20on%20the%20pedestal%20by%20the%20Left-Liberal-Secularist%20group%20and%20other%20anti-Modi%20forces.%20She%20has%20also%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20almost%20anything%20and%20everything%20relating%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20matter%20that%20Adani%20group%20businesses%20were%20expanding%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20country%20and%20many%20non-BJP%20state%20governments%20were%20rolling%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20the%20group%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20expos%C3%A9%20on%20Moitra's%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-query%26quot%3B%20exploded%20on%20the%20day%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20flagged%20in%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%2C%20Zhen%20Hua%2C%20as%20the%20first%20ship%20to%20dock%20at%20the%20Rs%207%2C700-crore%20deep%20water%20international%20seaport%20constructed%20as%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%20at%20Vizhinjam%20near%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20Vijayan%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame%20changer%26quot%3B%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20amusing%20to%20see%20both%20the%20CPM-led%20Left%20Front%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20opposition%20UDF%20fighting%20for%20credit%20for%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20made%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20against%20Mahua%20Moitra%20in%20his%20complaint%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20also%20sent%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%2C%20are%20alarming%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20A%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20complaint%2C%20which%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%2C%20jolts%20the%20conscience%20of%20any%20ordinary%20citizen.%20The%20sheer%20dichotomy%20between%20what%20she%20preaches%20and%20what%20she%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20made%20by%20Dehadrai%20against%20her%20were%20of%20a%20very%20serious%20nature%20-%20ethically%2C%20morally%2C%20politically%20and%20legally.%20She%20was%20accused%20of%20lending%20her%20parliamentary%20privileges%20and%20immunity%20to%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Hiranandani%20Group%2C%20to%20seek%20information%20relating%20to%20his%20businesses%20and%20also%2C%20settle%20scores%20with%20his%20business%20rival%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Dehadrai%20claims%20and%20meticulously%20lists%20each%20of%20them%20in%20his%20complaint%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%20Of%2061%20questions%20asked%20by%20Moitra%2C%2050%20were%20either%20related%20to%20the%20Hiranandani%20group's%20business%20interests%20or%20sought%20information%20on%20infra%20deals%20relating%20to%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20anybody's%20guess%20why%20such%20questions%20were%20asked%20and%20information%20sought%20from%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20damning%20is%20the%20allegation%20that%20she%20had%20shared%20full%20access%20to%20her%20login%20as%20an%20MP%20for%20anyone%20to%20post%20questions%20and%20seek%20answers%20from%20the%20government%20and%20to%20all%20other%20things%20that%20might%20be%20listed%20on%20the%20limited%20'authorised%20only'%20site.%20We%20know%20that%20since%20Covid%20Indian%20parliament%20has%20gradually%20become%20paperless%2C%20fully%20digital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20an%20MP's%20login%20by%20an%20unauthorised%20person%20raises%20implications%20related%20to%20the%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20parliamentary%20privileges%20and%20national%20security%20issues.%20In%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%2C%20Moitra%20said%20she%20would%20welcome%20a%20probe.%20The%20tone%20and%20tenor%20of%20her%20tweets%2C%20however%2C%20seemed%20to%20be%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20arrogance%20and%20smugness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiranandani%20has%20also%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20two%20days%2C%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20a%20vocal%20BJP%20MP%2C%20has%20written%20two%20letters%20and%20has%20only%20made%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20Moitra%20and%20for%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey's%20first%20letter%20was%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20on%20Sunday%2C%20calling%20it%20the%20re-emergence%20of%20%26quot%3BCash%20for%20Query%26quot%3B%20(in%20December%202005%2C%2011%20MPs%20were%20disqualified%20from%20parliament%20after%20an%20expose%20by%20the%20website%20Cobrapost)%20and%20seeking%20an%20investigation.%20He%20also%20urged%20the%20Speaker%20to%2C%20pending%20an%20inquiry%2C%20immediately%20restrict%20all%20access%20and%20privileges%20given%20to%20Moitra%20as%20an%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey's%20second%20letter%20went%20on%20Monday%20to%20Minister%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnav%2C%20copied%20to%20Minister%20of%20State%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar.%20In%20this%2C%20he%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20verify%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20lawyer%20Dehadrai%20that%20Moitra%20had%20given%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20access%20to%20Hiranandani.%20Dubey%20also%20called%20for%20a%20forensic%20investigation%20of%20IP%20addresses%20from%20where%20Moitra's%20account%20was%20accessed%2C%20to%20see%20if%20it%20matched%20her%20own%20location%20on%20those%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20is%20that%20Moitra%20did%20this%20in%20lieu%20of%20around%20Rs%202%20crore%20cash%20and%20extravagant%20gifts%20of%20super%20luxe%20brands%2C%20those%20that%20only%20about%20two%20to%20three%20per%20cent%20Indians%20would%20be%20familiar%20with%2C%20and%20only%20a%20minuscule%20can%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20are%20far%20more%20serious%20than%20the%202005%20cash-for-query%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20further%20complicated%20matters%20for%20Moitra%20is%20a%20response%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frajeev_goi%2Fstatus%2F1713866806727987442%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20on%20X%2C%20without%20naming%20either%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20or%20Hiranandani%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20parliamentary%20question%20on%20data%20localisation%20addressed%20to%20his%20ministry%20was%20the%20same%20for%20which%20a%20company%20was%20aggressively%20lobbying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20among%20Hiranandani%20Group%20companies%20is%20Yotta%20Data%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvents%20since%20Sunday%20afternoon%20suggest%20there%20could%20be%20multi-pronged%20inquiry%20by%20different%20agencies%20into%20the%20allegations.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20only%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20-%20Moitra's%20party%20boss%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20answer%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697539380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fdv3rd8do_mahua-moitra_625x300_02_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmahua-moitra-louis-vuitton-and-a-bagful-of-questions-4487889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20allegations%20made%20by%20Dehadrai%20against%20her%20were%20of%20a%20very%20serious%20nature%20-%20ethically%2C%20morally%2C%20politically%20and%20legally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmahua-moitra-louis-vuitton-and-a-bagful-of-questions-4487889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Test%20Flight%20For%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%20On%20Saturday.%20Read%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20on%20Tuesday%20posted%20details%20about%20Gaganyaan%20mission's%20Flight%20Test%20Vehicle%20Abort%20Mission-1%20(TV-D1)%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20The%20space%20agency%20said%20that%20the%20test%20is%20scheduled%20for%20October%2021%20(Saturday)%20at%208am%20and%20the%20vehicle%20will%20be%20launched%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20ISRO%20post%20further%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bshort-duration%20mission%26quot%3B.%20It%20further%20informed%20that%20registration%20to%20witness%20the%20launch%20will%20commence%20at%206pm%20on%20Tuesday.%20TV-D1%20will%20demonstrate%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20crew%20escape%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETV-D1%20Flight%20Test%3A%3Cbr%3E%20The%20test%20is%20scheduled%20for%20October%2021%2C%202023%2C%20at%200800%20Hrs.%20IST%20from%20the%20First%20launchpad%20at%20SDSC-SHAR%2C%20Sriharikota.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20It%20will%20be%20a%20short-duration%20mission%20and%20the%20visibility%20from%20the%20Launch%20View%20Gallery%20(LVG)%20will%20be%20limited.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Students%20and%20the%20Public%20can%20witness%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMROzlmPjRa%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMROzlmPjRa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1714208678675628360%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaganyaan%20project%20envisages%20a%20demonstration%20of%20ISRO's%20human%20spaceflight%20capability%20by%20launching%20a%20human%20crew%20to%20an%20orbit%20of%20400%20km%20and%20bringing%20them%20safely%20back%20to%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.isro.gov.in%2FFirst_Crew_Module_Gaganyaan_test_flight_TV_D1.html%5C%22%3EISRO%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20crew%20module%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20is%20in%20different%20stages%20of%20development.%20For%20TV-D1%2C%20the%20crew%20module%20is%20an%20unpressurised%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20houses%20all%20the%20systems%20for%20the%20deceleration%20and%20recovery%2C%20with%20its%20complete%20set%20of%20parachutes%2C%20recovery%20aids%20actuation%20systems%20and%20pyros%2C%20the%20website%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20that%20the%20crew%20module%20will%20be%20recovered%20after%20touchdown%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%2C%20using%20a%20dedicated%20vessel%20and%20diving%20team%20from%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20TV-D1%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20that%20the%20test%20vehicle%20is%20a%20single-stage%20liquid%20rocket%20developed%20for%20abort%20mission.%20The%20payloads%20consist%20of%20the%20crew%20module%20and%20crew%20escape%20systems%20with%20their%20fast-acting%20solid%20motors%2C%20along%20with%20CM%20fairing%20and%20interface%20adapters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20will%20simulate%20the%20abort%20condition%20during%20the%20ascent%20trajectory%20corresponding%20to%20a%20Mach%20number%20of%201.2%20encountered%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20escape%20system%20with%20crew%20module%20will%20be%20separated%20from%20the%20test%20vehicle%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20about%2017%20km.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20abort%20sequence%20will%20be%20executed%20autonomously%20commencing%20with%20the%20separation%20of%20CES%20and%20deployment%20of%20the%20series%20of%20parachutes%2C%20finally%20culminating%20in%20the%20safe%20touchdown%20of%20the%20crew%20module%20in%20the%20sea%2C%20about%2010%20km%20from%20the%20coast%20of%20Sriharikota%2C%20said%20ISRO.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697539320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Frni5oiko_gaganyaan-crew-launch-1200_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-test-flight-for-gaganyaan-mission-on-saturday-read-details-4489052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Through%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%2C%20ISRO%20plans%20to%20demonstrate%20its%20human%20spaceflight%20capability%20by%20sending%20a%20human%20crew%20to%20an%20orbit%20of%20400%20km%20and%20bringing%20them%20safely%20back%20to%20earth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-test-flight-for-gaganyaan-mission-on-saturday-read-details-4489052%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-test-flight-for-gaganyaan-mission-on-saturday-read-details-4489052%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-test-flight-for-gaganyaan-mission-on-saturday-read-details-4489052%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey's%20drones%20are%20a%20big%20hit%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20showing%20how%20they%20can%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224595%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayraktar%20TB2%20UAVs%20is%20seen%20during%20the%20test%20flight%20at%20the%20military%20base%20located%20in%20Hmelnitski%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20March%2020%2C%202019.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652d9d908bed706e837db51b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222297%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurkish-built%20Bayraktar%20TB2%20drones%20at%20a%20Ukrainian%20military%20base%20in%20March%202019.%3Cp%3EPress%20Office%20of%20the%20President%20of%20Ukraine%20%2F%20Mykola%20Lararenko%20%2F%20Handout%2FAnadolu%20Agency%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ETurkey's%20Bayraktar%20TB2%20drone%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20its%20performance%20against%20Russia%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBut%20Turkey%20has%20also%20deployed%20or%20sold%20