22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652da35055f52b01b360cd4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221053%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20and%20Syrian%20Democratic%20Forces%20troops%20on%20a%20patrol%20in%20northeast%20Syria%20in%20January%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FStaff%20Sgt.%20Jodi%20Eastham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EOn%20October%205%2C%20a%20Turkish%20drone%20bombing%20Kurdish%20targets%20came%20within%20about%20500%20yards%20of%20US%20troops%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeclared%20US%20restricted%20operating%20zone%26quot%3B%20near%20Hasakah%2C%20chief%20Pentagon%20spokesman%20Brig.%20Gen.%20Pat%20Ryder%2C%20said%20that%20day.%20The%20drone%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F05%2Fu-s-f-16-shoots-down-turkish-drone-flying-over-u-s-forces-in-syria-00120166%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20a%20TB2%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20deemed%20a%20threat%20and%20shot%20down%20by%20a%20US%20F-16%2C%20though%20Ryder%20said%20the%20US%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20indication%26quot%3B%20it%20was%20targeting%20US%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ETurkey%20initially%20denied%20the%20drone%20belonged%20to%20its%20military%20but%20later%20backtracked.%20In%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.tr%2Fno_-246_-irak-ve-suriye-de-pkk-ypg-teror-hedeflerine-yonelik-operasyonlarimiz-hk.en.mfa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%206%2C%20the%20Turkish%20Foreign%20Ministry%20confirmed%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20drone%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20different%20technical%20assessments%20in%20the%20deconfliction%20mechanism%20with%20third%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EThe%20statement%20was%20undoubtedly%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20US%2C%20as%20Turkey's%20military%20has%20separate%20de-escalation%20mechanisms%20with%20Russia%20and%20the%20US%20and%20requires%20a%20green%20light%20from%20at%20least%20one%20before%20launching%20major%20operations%20in%20Syria%2C%20which%20are%20invariably%20against%20the%20SDF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EUS%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20spoke%20to%20his%20Turkish%20counterpart%20after%20the%20shoot-down%20and%20%26quot%3Breaffirmed%20that%20the%20United%20States%20remains%20in%20Syria%20exclusively%20in%20support%20of%20the%20campaign%20to%20defeat%20ISIS%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryder%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.centcom.mil%2FMEDIA%2FNEWS-ARTICLES%2FNews-Article-View%2FArticle%2F3551081%2Fafter-us-downs-turkish-drone-in-syria-focus-remains-on-defeat-isis-mission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20Austin%20%26quot%3Bunderscored%20the%20importance%20of%20close%20coordination%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Turkey%20to%20prevent%20any%20risk%20to%20US%20forces%20or%20the%20global%20coalition's%20defeat-ISIS%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E'An%20unusual%20and%20extraordinary%20threat'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20Erdogan%20Biden%20NATO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652da3286561dd877e7bdd73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%20in%20Madrid%20in%20June%202022.%3Cp%3EGABRIEL%20BOUYS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EDespite%20such%20conciliatory%20statements%2C%20the%20US%20has%20said%20that%20Turkey's%20attacks%20on%20the%20SDF%2C%20including%20its%20current%20campaign%2C%20directly%20affect%20anti-ISIS%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EOn%20October%2012%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20extended%20a%20national%20emergency%20order%20on%20Syria%20declared%20by%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20following%20Turkey's%20October%202019%20cross-border%20offensive%20against%20the%20SDF%2C%20authorizing%20sanctions%20against%20Turkish%20officials%20involved%20in%20that%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2023%2F10%2F12%2Fnotice-on-the-continuation-of-the-national-emergency-with-respect-to-the-situation-in-and-in-relation-to-syria-3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20the%20extension%2C%20Biden%20cited%20%26quot%3Bactions%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Turkey%20to%20conduct%20a%20military%20offensive%20into%20northeast%20Syria%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20%26quot%3Bundermines%20the%20campaign%20to%20defeat%20the%20Islamic%20State%20of%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%2C%20or%20ISIS%2C%20endangers%20civilians%2C%20and%20further%20threatens%20to%20undermine%20the%20peace%2C%20security%2C%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EThose%20actions%2C%20Biden%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bpose%20an%20unusual%20and%20extraordinary%20threat%20to%20the%20national%20security%20and%20foreign%20policy%20of%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20government%20frequently%20touts%20its%20efforts%20to%20rally%20international%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20it%20undoubtedly%20welcomes%20the%20addition%20of%20Turkish%20TB2s%20Kyiv's%20arsenal.%20Conversely%2C%20in%20today's%20Middle%20East%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20divides%20between%20Turkey%20and%20its%20NATO%20allies%20are%20often%20on%20display%20%E2%80%94%20that%20very%20same%20drone%20is%20a%20hindrance%20or%20even%20a%20menace%20to%20the%20US's%20continued%20efforts%20to%20combat%20ISIS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Iddon%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20who%20writes%20about%20Middle%20East%20developments%2C%20military%20affairs%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20history.%20His%20articles%20have%20appeared%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20publications%20focused%20on%20the%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturkey-bayraktar-drones-praised-in-ukraine-pose-threat-elsewhere-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697539021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c97600eee94d001a78f503%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturkey-bayraktar-drones-praised-in-ukraine-pose-threat-elsewhere-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bayraktar%20TB2%20has%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20resistance%20for%20Ukrainians%2C%20but%20for%20other%20US%20partners%20it's%20not%20a%20welcome%20presence%20overhead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paul%20Iddon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturkey-bayraktar-drones-praised-in-ukraine-pose-threat-elsewhere-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Countries%20Where%20Homosexuality%20Can%20Lead%20To%20Capital%20Punishment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20today%20stopped%20short%20of%20legalising%20marriage%20equality%20but%20stressed%20that%20an%20individual's%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20union%20cannot%20be%20restricted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sexual%20orientation.%20The%20five-judge%20bench%20came%20up%20with%20four%20judgments%2C%20differing%20primarily%20on%20the%20question%20of%20adoption%20rights%20for%20queer%20couples.%20The%20judges%20asked%20the%20centre%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20address%20practical%20concerns%20of%20same-sex%20couples%2C%20such%20as%20getting%20ration%20cards%2C%20pensions%2C%20gratuities%2C%20and%20succession%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20been%20dealt%20with%20very%20differently%20across%20the%20world%2C%20with%20at%20least%2010%20countries%20bordering%20on%20punishing%20homosexuality%20with%20the%20death%20penalty.%20In%20certain%20instances%2C%20this%20harsh%20sentencing%20is%20rooted%20in%20religious%20laws.%20There%20are%20also%20cases%20where%20laws%20permitting%20the%20death%20penalty%20exist%20but%20have%20not%20been%20enforced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20list%20outlines%2010%20countries%20where%20homosexuality%20could%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20death%20penalty%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYemen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%2C%20quoting%20the%201994%20penal%20code%2C%20that%20married%20men%20can%20be%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20stoning%20for%20homosexual%20intercourse.%20Unmarried%20men%20face%20whipping%20or%20one%20year%20in%20prison.%20Women%20face%20up%20to%20seven%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20sharia%20law%2C%20homosexual%20intercourse%20between%20men%20can%20be%20punished%20by%20death%2C%20and%20men%20can%20be%20flogged%20for%20lesser%20acts%20such%20as%20kissing.%20Women%20may%20be%20flogged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMauritania%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20African%20nation%20of%20Mauritania%2C%20a%201984%20law%20dictates%20that%20Muslim%20men%20found%20involved%20in%20homosexual%20activities%20may%20face%20execution%20by%20stoning%2C%20although%20no%20such%20executions%20have%20occurred%20to%20date.%20Women%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20be%20sentenced%20to%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20same%20offense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20is%20the%20sole%20nation%20on%20the%20African%20continent%20to%20allow%20gay%20marriage%2C%20which%20it%20legalised%20in%202006.%20Gay%20sex%20is%20decriminalised%20in%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20countries%3A%20Angola%2C%20Lesotho%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20and%20the%20Seychelles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENigeria%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENigeria's%20federal%20penal%20code%20penalises%20homosexual%20acts%20with%20death%20or%20flogging.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2016%2F06%2F13%2Fhere-are-the-10-countries-where-homosexuality-may-be-punished-by-death-2%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20federal%20law%20classifies%20homosexual%20behavior%20as%20a%20felony%20punishable%20by%20imprisonment%2C%20but%20several%20states%20have%20adopted%20sharia%20law%20and%20imposed%20a%20death%20penalty%20for%20men.%20A%20law%20signed%20in%20early%20January%20makes%20it%20illegal%20for%20gay%20people%20countrywide%20to%20hold%20a%20meeting%20or%20form%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQatar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharia%20law%20in%20Qatar%20applies%20only%20to%20Muslims%2C%20who%20can%20be%20put%20to%20death%20for%20extramarital%20sex%2C%20regardless%20of%20sexual%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaudi%20Arabia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20country's%20interpretation%20of%20sharia%20law%2C%20a%20married%20man%20engaging%20in%20same%20sex%20relationship%20or%20any%20non-Muslim%20who%20commits%20gay%20relationships%C2%A0%20with%20a%20Muslim%20can%20be%20stoned%20to%20death.%20All%20sex%20outside%20of%20marriage%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20in%20countries%20like%20Afghanistan%2C%20Somalia%2C%20and%20Sudan%2C%20the%20sharia%20law%20criminalises%20same-sex%20sexual%20acts%20with%20a%20maximum%20of%20the%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20experts%20disagree%20on%20whether%20federal%20law%20prescribes%20the%20death%20penalty%20for%20consensual%20homosexual%20sex%20or%20only%20for%20rape.%20In%20a%20recent%20Amnesty%20International%20report%2C%20the%20organization%20said%20it%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20death%20sentences%20for%20homosexual%20acts.%20All%20sexual%20acts%20outside%20of%20marriage%20are%20banned%2C%20according%20to%20the%20media%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697538960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F49suusb8_lgbtq-event-_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-countries-where-homosexuality-can-lead-to-capital-punishment-4489006%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20countries%20have%20banned%20homosexuality%2C%20with%20many%20of%20them%20having%20the%20death%20penalty%20for%20same-sex%20relations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-countries-where-homosexuality-can-lead-to-capital-punishment-4489006%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-countries-where-homosexuality-can-lead-to-capital-punishment-4489006%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-countries-where-homosexuality-can-lead-to-capital-punishment-4489006%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Comedian%20Nishant%20Suri%20Cancels%20Bengaluru%20Show%20Over%20Non-Payment%20By%20Organisers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20in%20Bengaluru%20was%20left%20disappointed%20after%20stand-up%20comedian%20Nishant%20Suri%20cancelled%20his%20show%20on%20October%2013%20over%20non-payment%20of%20dues%20by%20the%20event%20organisers.%20The%20winner%20of%20Comicstaan%20Season%201%20took%20to%20Instagram%20and%20said%20that%20the%20organisers%20The%20Entertainment%20Factory%2C%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20sending%20a%20forged%20screenshot%20of%20the%20money%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20the%20comedian%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20already%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20and%20this%