0if%20he%20is%20made%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20his%20forthright%20and%20honest%20speech%20will%20cost%20him%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYe%20makan%20ya%20dukan%20ki%20nahin%2C%20Samvidhan%20ko%20bachane%20ki%20ladhayi%20hai%3Cbr%3E%20In%20the%20end%2C%20truth%20and%20justice%20have%20prevailed%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20My%20statement%20on%20the%20Hon'ble%20Delhi%20High%20Court's%20ruling%20to%20set%20aside%20the%20unjust%20order%20to%20evict%20me%20from%20my%20official%20residence.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfA7BJ2zLYm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfA7BJ2zLYm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Raghav%20Chadha%20(%40raghav_chadha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fraghav_chadha%2Fstatus%2F1714223183459660149%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Anup%20Jairam%20Bhambhani%20has%20revived%20an%20April%2018%20order%20of%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20which%20had%20directed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20not%20to%20evict%20Mr%20Chadha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20had%20ruled%20that%20Mr%20Chadha%20does%20not%20have%20an%20absolute%20right%20to%20continue%20to%20occupy%20his%20government%20bungalow%20during%20his%20entire%20tenure%20as%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20even%20after%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20allotment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20agreed%20to%20hear%20Mr%20Chadha's%20case%2C%20challenging%20his%20suspension%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Mr%20Chadha%20was%20suspended%20for%20allegedly%20forging%20signatures%20of%20other%20MPs%20and%20proposing%20their%20names%20for%20a%20committee%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20instructed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20secretariat%20to%20address%20the%20accusations%20and%20has%20also%20requested%20the%20assistance%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%20R%20Venkataramani.%20The%20case%20will%20be%20resumed%20on%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20August%20after%20four%20MPs%20accused%20him%20of%20including%20their%20names%20in%20a%20committee%20without%20their%20consent.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697538420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fm0q29bo8_raghav-chadha_625x300_17_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-raghav-chadha-wont-have-to-vacate-government-bungalow-gets-court-relief-4488682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20will%20not%20have%20to%20vacate%20his%20government%20bungalow%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20set%20aside%20a%20trial%20court%20order%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-raghav-chadha-wont-have-to-vacate-government-bungalow-gets-court-relief-4488682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-raghav-chadha-wont-have-to-vacate-government-bungalow-gets-court-relief-4488682%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-raghav-chadha-wont-have-to-vacate-government-bungalow-gets-court-relief-4488682%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20than%204%20out%20of%205%20of%20bosses%20are%20'accidental%20managers'%20who%20stumble%20into%20leadership%20with%20little%20training%2C%20a%20UK%20survey%20found%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Office%20workers%20at%20Canary%20Wharf%20in%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652e4b4c69c17ca46ae826ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20third%20of%20managers%20said%20they've%20never%20received%20formal%20management%20or%20leadership%20training%2C%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20Chartered%20Management%20Institute%20found.%20%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAround%2082%25%20of%20bosses%20lack%20any%20formal%20leadership%20or%20management%20training%20and%20qualifications.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20survey%20by%20the%20Chartered%20Management%20Institute%20surveyed%20over%204%2C500%20managers%20and%20workers%20in%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHalf%20of%20the%20managers%20surveyed%20said%20promotions%20are%20given%20based%20on%20internal%20relationships%20over%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20manager%20and%20senior%20leaders%20at%20your%20company%20are%20unlikely%20to%20have%20any%20formal%20qualifications%20or%20training%20for%20that%20position%2C%20a%20worrying%20new%20survey%20has%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chartered%20Management%20Institute%20released%20a%20nationwide%20study%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.managers.org.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FCMI_BMB_GoodManagment_Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUK%20management%20and%20leadership%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October.%20It%20commissioned%20YouGov%20to%20survey%20over%204%2C500%20managers%20and%20employees%20online%20in%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20although%20one%20in%20four%20people%20in%20the%20workforce%20takes%20on%20management%20responsibilities%2C%2082%25%20of%20those%20who%20become%20managers%20have%20little%20training%20or%20qualification.%20They're%20called%20%26quot%3Baccidental%20managers%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20survey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20half%20of%20managers%20said%20they%20don't%20hold%20any%20management%20or%20leadership%20qualifications%20and%20a%20third%20said%20they%20had%20never%20received%20formal%20management%20and%20leadership%20training.%20This%20also%20applied%20to%2026%25%20of%20senior%20managers%20and%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20number%20of%20workers%20promoted%20to%20leadership%20positions%20without%20real%20experience%20can%20partly%20be%20attributed%20to%20favoritism%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20the%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20half%20of%20the%20managers%20said%20promotions%20were%20dished%20out%20based%20on%20internal%20relationships%20and%20profile%20rather%20than%20ability%20and%20performance%2C%20per%20CMI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20a%20third%20said%20people%20who%20spent%20more%20time%20in%20the%20office%20with%20managers%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20progress%20as%20well.%20This%20trend%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbosses-worry-proximity-bias-hurt-remote-employees-career-progression-2021-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eproximity%20bias%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20sees%20remote%20employees%20overlooked%20for%20promotions%20because%20they're%20not%20as%20visible%20to%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoor%20managers%20are%20contributing%20to%20high%20employee%20turnover%20as%20well.%C2%A0%20Only%2027%25%20of%20workers%20rated%20their%20manager%20as%20highly%20effective%20and%2037%25%20said%20they're%20somewhat%20effective%2C%20the%20CMI%20survey%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20findings%20from%20the%20survey%20included%20that%20half%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20did%20not%20think%20their%20manager%20was%20effective%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20leave%20in%20the%20next%2012%20months%20compared%20to%2021%25%20of%20workers%20who%20did%20see%20their%20manager%20as%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%2031%25%20of%20managers%20and%2028%25%20of%20workers%20had%20left%20a%20job%20because%20of%20a%20negative%20relationship%20with%20their%20boss.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fservices%2F182216%2Fstate-ameri