vour%20of%20the%20queer%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Good%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20five-judge%20bench's%20refusal%20to%20legalise%20same-sex%20marriages%20is%20based%20not%20on%20an%20in-principle%20opposition%20to%20marriage%20equality%2C%20but%20on%20legal%20technicalities%20and%20concerns%20of%20judicial%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20judges%20agreed%20the%20queer%20couples%20are%20neither%20urban%20nor%20elitist%2C%20countering%20an%20argument%20of%20the%20centre%20during%20the%20hearing%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20also%20noted%20the%20centre's%20submission%20that%20a%20panel%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%20will%20look%20into%20practical%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20same-sex%20couples.%20The%20bench%20agreed%20that%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20queer%20couples%20in%20accessing%20basic%20services%20are%20discriminatory%20in%20nature%20and%20said%20the%20government%20panel%20must%20look%20into%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Do%20Petitioners%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20judgment%2C%20Geeta%20Luthra%2C%20senior%20advocate%20and%20counsel%20for%20several%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20right%20to%20marriage%20has%20not%20been%20given%2C%20CJI%20has%20said%20that%20the%20same%20bundle%20of%20rights%20which%20every%20married%20couple%20has%20should%20be%20available%20to%20same-sex%20couples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELGBTQIA%2B%20rights%20activist%20Harish%20Iyer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20also%20noted%20the%20observations%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20queer%20community.%20%26quot%3BThough%20at%20the%20end%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20not%20in%20our%20favour%20but%2C%20so%20many%20observations%20made%20were%20in%20our%20favour.%20They%20have%20also%20put%20the%20responsibility%20on%20the%20central%20government.%20The%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20so%20many%20things%20against%20us%2C%20so%20it%20is%20important%20for%20us%20to%20go%20to%20our%20elected%20government%2C%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20and%20tell%20them%20we%20are%20as%20different%20as%20two%20people.%20War%20is%20underway...%20it%20might%20take%20sometime%20but%20we%20will%20get%20societal%20equality%2C%26quot%3B%20ANI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnjali%20Gopalan%2C%20petitioner%20and%20activist%2C%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20fighting%20for%20long%20and%20will%20keep%20doing%20so%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BRegarding%20adoption%20also%20nothing%20was%20done%2C%20what%20the%20CJI%20said%20was%20very%20good%20regarding%20adoption%2C%20but%20it's%20disappointing%20that%20other%20justices%20didn't%20agree...%20This%20is%20democracy%20but%20we%20are%20denying%20basic%20rights%20to%20our%20own%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fngsh0jtg_supreme-court_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcerns%20Of%20Delay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20had%20in%20May%20submitted%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20panel%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%20to%20look%20into%20practical%20issues%20faced%20by%20same-sex%20couples%20in%20accessing%20services%20such%20as%20Provident%20Fund%20and%20pension.%20Following%20that%20submission%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20update%20on%20whether%20this%20panel%20met%20and%20held%20discussions%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERights%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20are%20not%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20but%20any%20move%20on%20this%20matter%20can%20have%20significant%20political%20ramifications.%20Also%2C%20any%20step%20towards%20legalising%20same-sex%20marriages%20is%20bound%20to%20face%20resistance%20from%20within%20the%20society%2C%20including%20religious%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20country%20gearing%20up%20for%20a%20general%20election%20next%20year%2C%20same-sex%20couples%20and%20their%20rights%20may%20not%20feature%20high%20on%20the%20government's%20priority%20list%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20political%20impact%20any%20such%20move%20may%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Observations%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20stressed%20that%20an%20individual's%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20union%20cannot%20be%20restricted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sexual%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20however%2C%20underlined%20that%20the%20court%20must%20be%20careful%20to%20not%20enter%20the%20legislative%20domain%2C%20and%20said%20it%20is%20for%20Parliament%20to%20decide%20if%20changes%20are%20needed%20in%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20challenged%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20some%20provisions%20of%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20Foreign%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20and%20other%20marriage%20laws%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20they%20deny%20same-sex%20couples%20the%20right%20to%20marry.%20They%20had%20requested%20the%20court%20to%20read%20these%20provisions%20broadly%20to%20include%20same-sex%20marriage.%20The%20court%20had%20earlier%20clarified%20that%20it%20will%20not%20go%20into%20personal%20laws%20and%20only%20look%20at%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20backed%20same-sex%20couples'%20right%20to%20adopt%20children%2C%20a%20stand%20opposed%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20judges%20on%20the%20bench.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaw%20cannot%20assume%20that%20only%20heterosexual%20couples%20can%20be%20good%20parents.%20This%20would%20amount%20to%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20questioning%20the%20current%20norms%20that%20bar%20queer%20couples%20from%20adopting%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20listed%20several%20directions%20for%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20government%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20ensure%20queer%20couples%20are%20not%20discriminated%20against%20and%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20queer%20rights%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%20said%20non-heterosexual%20unions%20and%20heterosexual%20unions%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20seen%20as%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20this%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20%26quot%3Bremedy%20historical%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20grant%20recognition%20to%20such%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReading%20out%20the%20majority%20judgment%20that%20differed%20with%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justice%20Kaul%20on%20the%20question%20of%20adoption%2C%20Justice%20S%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20agreed%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20%26quot%3Bqueerness%20is%20neither%20urban%20nor%20elitist%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20difficulties%20in%20creating%20through%20a%20judicial%20diktat%20a%20right%20to%20civil%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cannot%20create%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20queer%20couples%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20legislature%20to%20do%20as%20there%20are%20several%20aspects%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERuling%20out%20any%20tweak%20in%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20gender%20neutral%20interpretation%20of%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20may%20not%20be%20equitable%20at%20times%20and%20can%20result%20in%20women%20being%20exposed%20to%20vulnerabilities%20in%20an%20unintended%20manner.%26quot%3B%20The%20judge%20agreed%20that%20denial%20of%20benefits%20such%20as%20Provident%20Fund%2C%20pension%20etc%20to%20queer%20partners%20may%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Badverse%20discriminatory%20effect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposing%20the%20minority%20judgment%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20extending%20adoption%20rights%20to%20same-sex%20couples%2C%20Justice%20Bhat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20unmarried%20or%20non-heterosexual%20couples%20can't%20be%20good%20parents...%20given%20the%20objective%20of%20section%2057%2C%20the%20State%20as%20parens%20patriae%20has%20to%20explore%20all%20areas%20and%20to%20ensure%20all%20benefits%20reach%20the%20children%20at%20large%20in%20need%20of%20stable%20homes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20PS%20Narasimha%2C%20who%20agreed%20with%20Justice%20Bhat%2C%20said%20a%20review%20of%20legislative%20schemes%20that%20excludes%20same-sex%20partners%20from%20pension%2C%20PF%2C%20gratuity%20and%20insurance%20benefits%20was%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697537700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F48akc36g_india-pride-paradelgbtq650_625x300_07_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsame-sex-marriage-marriage-equality-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-supreme-courts-judgment-on-same-sex-marriage-reading-between-the-lines-4488853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20surface%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20not%20legalise%20same-sex%20marriages%20or%20extend%20adoption%20rights%20to%20queer%20couples%20may%20appear%20disappointing%2C%20but%20read%20between%20the%20lines%2C%20and%20there%20is%20much%20to%20cheer%20about.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsame-sex-marriage-marriage-equality-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-supreme-courts-judgment-on-same-sex-marriage-reading-between-the-lines-4488853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsame-sex-marriage-marriage-equality-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-supreme-courts-judgment-on-same-sex-marriage-reading-between-the-lines-4488853%2Famp%2F