very%20100%20entry-level%20men.%3Cp%3E10'000%20Hours%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20Lean%20In%20and%20McKinsey%20report%20found%20that%20fewer%20women%20than%20men%20in%20entry-level%20jobs%20were%20promoted%20to%20manager.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELean%20In's%20CEO%20said%20fixing%20the%20%26quot%3Bbroken%20rung%26quot%3B%20would%20mean%20more%20women%20representation%20in%20the%20work%20pipeline.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOne%20thing%20that%20can%20be%20done%20is%20to%20remind%20people%20about%20biases%20ahead%20of%20promotion%20cycles.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-women-careers-jobs-pandemic-flexibility-gender-equality-2023-7%5C%22%3EWomen%3C%2Fa%3E's%20largest%20obstacle%20to%20career%20advancement%20is%20reaching%20the%20next%20rung%20on%20the%20ladder.%20A%20new%20study%20found%20that%20women%20are%20less%20likely%20than%20men%20to%20move%20up%20and%20become%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20the%20ninth%20annual%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleanin.org%2Fwomen-in-the-workplace%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%20in%20the%20Workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20report%20by%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20and%20Lean%20In%2C%20which%20collected%20information%C2%A0on%20gender%20at%20work%20in%202022%C2%A0from%20276%20organizations%20employing%20over%2010%20million%20people.%20The%20report%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20every%20100%20men%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-get-promotion-raise-ask-pitch-boss-career-coach-tips-2023-2%5C%22%3Epromoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20entry%20level%20to%20manager%2C%2087%20women%20were%20promoted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20have%20this%20laser%20focus%20typically%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fglass-ceiling%5C%22%3Eglass%20ceiling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what%20we%20need%20is%20a%20laser%20focus%20on%20the%20broken%20rung%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexis%20Krivkovich%2C%20a%20senior%20partner%20for%20McKinsey%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20very%20first%20step%20up%20to%20manager%20still%20after%20all%20these%20years%20is%20the%20most%20inequitable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachel%20Thomas%2C%20CEO%20of%20Lean%20In%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20fixing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsheryl-sandberg-mckinsey-research-on-broken-rung-for-black-women-2020-8%5C%22%3Ebroken%20rung%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20mean%20more%20women%20managers%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20upward%20momentum%20in%20the%20talent%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FWh6er%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20the%20corporate%20pipeline%20at%20the%20start%20of%202023%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20companies%20are%20increasing%20women's%20representation%20at%20the%20top%2C%20doing%20so%20without%20addressing%20the%20broken%20rung%20offers%20only%20a%20temporary%20stopgap%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20stated.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20gender%20disparity%20in%20early%20promotions%2C%20men%20end%20up%20holding%2060%25%20of%20manager-level%20positions%20in%20a%20typical%20company%2C%20while%20women%20occupy%2040%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20further%20up%20the%20ladder%2C%20women%20occupy%20only%2036%25%20of%20senior%20manager%20or%20director%20roles%20and%2028%25%20of%20C-suite%20positions%20at%20the%20companies%20analyzed%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrivkovich%20said%20that%20for%20women%20of%20color%2C%20the%20number%20who%20are%20promoted%20from%20entry-level%20to%20manager%20level%20relative%20to%20every%20100%20men%20%26quot%3Bis%20even%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FFsG0Z%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20number%20of%20women%20promoted%20for%20every%20100%20men%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broken%20rung%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20never-ending%20problem.%20Thomas%20and%20Krivkovich%20agreed%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20remove%20the%20hurdles%20for%20women%20looking%20to%20climb%20professionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20employers%20can%20remind%20managers%20and%20those%20conducting%20promotions%20about%20potential%20biases%20they%20may%20have%20ahead%20of%20promotion%20cycles%2C%20Thomas%20said.%20Companies%20should%20look%20at%20the%20women%20being%20promoted%2C%20the%20promotion%20outcomes%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthose%20metrics%20by%20race%20and%20gender%20so%20that%20women%20of%20color%20are%20not%20inadvertently%20overlooked%26quot%3B%20for%20advancement%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20really%20simple%20thing%20they%20can%20do%20is%20ask%20evaluators%20to%20explain%20their%20rationale%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20from%20research%20that%20when%20you%20have%20to%20explain%20why%20you%20rated%20someone%20a%20certain%20way%20or%20why%20you%20gave%20input%20on%20their%20performance%20that%20you%20did%2C%20that%20it%20really%20allows%20you%20to%20step%20back%20and%20think%20critically%20about%20your%20own%20evaluation%20and%20de-bias%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20also%20said%20given%20the%20%26quot%3Bbroken%20rung%20is%20more%20broken%20for%20women%20of%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20should%20also%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20laser%20focus%20on%20women%20of%20color%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20there%20are%20career%20development%20and%20mentorship%20and%20sponsorship%20programs%20designed%20specifically%20to%20address%20the%20distinct%20bias%20and%20barriers%20they're%20facing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpromotions-women-face-broken-rung-early-on-in-corporate-ladder-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697537341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65283e1d68f1d46f52b06059%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpromotions-women-face-broken-rung-early-on-in-corporate-ladder-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Lean%20In%20and%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20report%20found%20fewer%20entry-level%20women%20than%20men%20were%20promoted%20based%20on%20data%20from%20over%20200%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpromotions-women-face-broken-rung-early-on-in-corporate-ladder-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Liam%20Gallagher%20Sets%2030th%20Anniversary%20Celebration%20Tour%20for%20Oasis%20Debut%20Album%20%E2%80%98Definitely%20Maybe%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697537102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLiam-Gallagher.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235758743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Liam%20Gallagher%20has%20revealed%20a%202024%20U.K.%20and%20Ireland%20tour%20to%20celebrate%20the%2030th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20first%20Oasis%20album%20%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20Maybe.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20bouncing%20around%20the%20house%20to%20announce%20the%20%E2%80%98Definitely%20Maybe%E2%80%99%20tour.%20The%20most%20important%20album%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%20bar%20none.%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20anywhere%20without%20it%20and%20neither%20would%20you%2C%20so%20let%E2%80%99s%20celebrate%20%5B%E2%80%A6%