%20of%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%20on%20October%2012%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%5C%22%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20War%20Is%20a%20Stain%20on%20Every%20One%20of%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20noticed%20that%20the%20viral%20videos%20contain%20an%20Arabic%20watermark%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20Momen%20El%20Halabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMomen%20El%20Halabi%20is%20a%20Palestinian%20photographer%20who%20has%20been%20covering%20and%20documenting%20the%20Israeli%20atrocities%20on%20Palestinians.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20trace%20the%20viral%20video%20back%20to%20his%20Instagram%20account%2C%20where%20he%20had%20initially%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyTR-DFoXDS%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20reached%20out%20to%20Momen%20who%20refuted%20the%20viral%20claim%20that%20the%20photo%20showed%20a%20doll%20and%20not%20an%20actual%20child.%20He%20told%20Alt%20News%20that%20the%20boy%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20was%204-year-old%20Omar%20Bilal%20Al-Banna%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Al-Zaytoun%20neighbourhood%2C%20east%20of%20Gaza%20City.%20He%20also%20shared%20several%20other%20pictures%20of%20Omar%20with%20us%20for%20further%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-trans%3D%5C%22fade%5C%22%20data-gallery%3D%5C%22%5B%7B%26quot%3Bsrc%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fmomeen4.jpg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bid%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B168385%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Btitle%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bmomeen4%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Balt%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bcaption%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bitemprop%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%26quot%3B%7D%2C%7B%26quot%3Bsrc%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fmomeen3.jpg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bid%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B168386%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Btitle%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bmomeen3%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Balt%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bcaption%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bitemprop%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%26quot%3B%7D%2C%7B%26quot%3Bsrc%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fmomeen2.jpg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bid%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B168387%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Btitle%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bmomeen2%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Balt%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bcaption%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bitemprop%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%26quot%3B%7D%2C%7B%26quot%3Bsrc%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fmomeen1.jpg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bid%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B168388%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Btitle%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bmomeen1%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Balt%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bcaption%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bitemprop%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%26quot%3B%7D%5D%5C%22%20data-autostart%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20air%20raids%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2023%2Foct%2F11%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-updates-death-toll-us-egypt-passage-gaza%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CThe%2520ministry%2520said%2520the%2520strikes%2520hit%2520Sabra%252C%2520Al%2520Zaytoun%252C%2520Al%2520Nafaq%2520and%2520Tal%2520Al%2520Hawa.%2520A%2520separate%2520report%2520said%2520Gaza%25E2%2580%2599s%2520Khan%2520Younis%2520was%2520also%2520hit%2520by%2520air%2520strikes.%2520Search%2520and%2520rescue%2520operations%2520are%2520reportedly%2520under%2520way%252C%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Al%20Zaytoun%20in%20Gaza%20on%20October%2012.%20This%20corroborates%20the%20date%20of%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20i.e.%2C%20October%2012%2C%20(as%20seen%20on%20Getty%20Images).%20The%20place%20where%20he%20was%20killed%2C%20Al%20Zaytoun%2C%20was%20among%20the%20places%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%2C%20alongside%20Al%20Nafaq%2C%20Sabra%2C%20and%20Tal%20Al%20Hawa%2C%20leaving%2051%20dead%20and%20281%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20informed%20by%20Momen%20that%20the%20men%20in%20the%20grey%20t-shirt%20and%20red%20t-shirt%20seen%20with%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20body%20were%20his%20relatives.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20child%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20occupation%20in%20previous%20years%E2%80%9D%2C%20Momen%20said.%20He%20also%20sent%20us%20the%20raw%2C%20full%20version%20of%20the%20viral%20footage%20of%20Omar%20being%20carried%20by%20the%20relative%2C%20sans%20the%20background%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20clarify%20that%20the%20child%20seen%20in%20the%20pictures%20Momen%20sent%20us%20is%20the%20same%20child%20seen%20in%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20we%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20distinct%20marks%20on%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20face%2C%20two%20on%20his%20forehead%20and%20one%20on%20his%20chin.%20We%20have%20blurred%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeveral%20Reports%20Place%20Grey%20T-Shirt%20Man%20on%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20Premises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20we%20found%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimesofgaza%2Fstatus%2F1712477921280131310%3Ft%3DeG0inwDN63xWBDigOnK4UQ%26s%3D19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0tweet%20dated%20October%2012%2C%20containing%20an%20image%20of%20the%20man%20in%20the%20grey%20t-shirt%20(seen%20with%20Omar%20in%20the%20photos%20and%20videos%20above)%20carrying%20a%20body%20wrapped%20in%20white%20cloth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20could%20locate%20the%20place%20where%20the%20image%20was%20clicked.%20We%20found%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.ap.org%2Feditorial-photos-videos%2Fdetail%3Fitemid%3D700c611623484945a2ad07028067c647%26mediatype%3Dvideo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shot%20in%20the%20same%20place%2C%20dated%20October%208.%20The%20video%20pans%20out%20to%20show%20the%20name%20%E2%80%9CAl-Shifa%20Medical%20Complex%E2%80%9D%20inscribed%20on%20a%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpalestine-solidarity-jantar-mantar-india%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98In%20Standing%20With%20Palestine%2C%20We%20Are%20Also%20Standing%20Up%20For%20Ourselves%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20implies%20that%20the%20man%20was%20actually%20at%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%2C%20as%20has%20been%20corroborated%20by%20the%20Getty%20Images%20caption%2C%20and%20also%20independently%20to%20Alt%20News%20by%20photographer%20Momen%20El%20Halabi%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20spot%20and%20recorded%20the%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOthers%20Who%20Shared%20the%20False%20Claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dhamas%2Bshares%2Bvideo%2Bof%2Bdoll%26sca_esv%3D573754553%26rlz%3D1C1VDKB_enIN1019IN1019%26biw%3D1454%26bih%3D795%26tbm%3Dnws%26ei%3D0xQtZeiDAuDWseMP4IOnsA4%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiouYSYsvqBAxVga2wGHeDBCeYQ4dUDCA0%26uact%3D5%26oq%3Dhamas%2Bshares%2Bvideo%2Bof%2Bdoll%26gs_lp%3DEgxnd3Mtd2l6LW5ld3MiGmhhbWFzIHNoYXJlcyB2aWRlbyBvZiBkb2xsSKpAUPwfWIg_cAF4AJABAJgBtwKgAb0iqgEIMC4xOC40LjG4AQPIAQD4AQHCAgUQIRigAcICBBAAGAPCAgYQABgDGArCAg4QABiKBRixAxiDARiRAsICCxAAGIoFGLEDGIMBwgILEAAYgAQYsQMYgwHCAgUQABiABMICBhAAGBYYHsICCBAAGBYYHhgPwgIKEAAYFhgeGA8YCsICCBAAGIoFGIYDwgIHECEYoAEYCogGAQ%26sclient%3Dgws-wiz-news%5C%22%3ESeveral%20news%20media%20outlets%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20reports%20on%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20apparent%20tactic%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdeception%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%