%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZipcar%20let%20customers%20rent%20Ford%20Transit%20vans%20that%20were%20being%20recalled%2C%20the%20NHTSA%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20vans%20were%20being%20recalled%20over%20a%20safety%20issue%20that%20could%20make%20them%20lose%20power%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZipcar%20has%20been%20fined%20%24300%2C000%20over%20the%20violation%2C%20the%20NHTSA%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECar-sharing%20company%20Zipcar%20has%20been%20fined%20%24300%2C000%20for%20renting%20out%20vehicles%20that%20were%20being%20recalled%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhtsa.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Fnhtsa-announces-consent-order-zipcar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Highway%20Traffic%20and%20Safety%20Administration%2C%20or%20NHTSA%2C%20said%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NHTSA%20said%20in%20a%20consent%20order%20that%20Zipcar%20had%20allowed%20customers%20to%20rent%202015-2017%20models%20of%20the%20Ford%20Transit%2C%20after%20a%20recall%20had%20been%20issued%20for%20the%20vehicles%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhtsa.gov%2Frecall-spotlight%2Fford-0%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSummary%26amp%3Btext%3DFord%2520Motor%2520Company%2520(Ford)%2520is%2Cthe%2520driveshaft%2520may%2520prematurely%2520fail.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJune%202017%20over%20safety%20issues.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20was%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20flexible%20coupling%20between%20the%20transmission%20and%20driveshaft%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20vans%20could%20crack%20with%20extended%20use%2C%20causing%20the%20vehicles%20to%20potentially%20lose%20power%20on%20the%20road%20or%20start%20moving%20in%20park%20if%20the%20parking%20brake%20wasn't%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NHTSA's%20consent%20order%20to%20Zipcar%20is%20the%20result%20of%20an%20investigation%20opened%20by%20the%20agency%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20agency's%20employees%20said%20they%20had%20rented%20a%20van%20from%20Zipcar%20in%20July%202017%2C%20only%20to%20discover%20the%20vehicle%20had%20an%20open%20recall%20that%20the%20car-sharing%20firm%20hadn't%20told%20them%20about%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.nhtsa.gov%2Fodi%2Finv%2F2018%2FINIM-AQ18001-71738.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20NHTSA%20records.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20later%20concluded%20that%20Zipcar%20had%20rented%20out%20recalled%20Ford%20Transits%20up%20until%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVehicles%20with%20open%2C%20unrepaired%20recalls%20pose%20a%20safety%20risk%20to%20everyone%20on%20the%20road.%20NHTSA%20takes%20violations%20of%20the%20Safety%20Act%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20Ann%20Carlson%2C%20the%20acting%20administrator%20for%20the%20NHTSA%2C%20said%20in%20the%20agency's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20fine%2C%20Zipcar%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20send%20an%20audit%20report%20to%20the%20NHTSA%20on%20all%20Zipcar%20vehicles%20with%20open%20recalls%20within%20150%20days%20of%20the%20consent%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car-sharing%20firm%20will%20also%20have%20to%20revise%20its%20staff%20training%20on%20recalls%2C%20and%20have%20the%20updates%20assessed%20by%20third-party%20lawyers%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20NHTSA%20for%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Zipcar%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fzipcar-consent-order-car-recalls-nhsta-c648e4f10d53a362cd5e3a31dd022891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20fewer%20than%2050%20cars%20in%20its%20global%20fleet%20of%2012%2C000%20vehicles%20%26quot%3Bwere%20found%20in%20violation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Zipcar%2C%20we%20prioritize%20our%20members'%20safety%20and%20take%20manufacturers'%20recalls%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzipcar-fined-renting-recalled-ford-transits-nhtsa-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697534255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652e50ea69c17ca46ae828a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzipcar-fined-renting-recalled-ford-transits-nhtsa-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20NHTSA%20employee%20had%20rented%20a%20van%20from%20Zipcar%20in%202017%2C%20only%20to%20find%20out%20the%20vehicle%20had%20an%20open%20recall%20the%20company%20didn't%20tell%20them%20about%2C%20per%20NHTSA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40insider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzipcar-fined-renting-recalled-ford-transits-nhtsa-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Transparency%20in%20Modi%20Era%3F%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20Working%20Shows%20It%20Remains%20Opaque%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03200823%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-8.07.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20is%20the%20supreme%20audit%20institution%20of%20India%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20promote%20financial%20accountability%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20audited%20entities%2C%20the%20CAG%20said%20in%20its%202019-20%20performance%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20stranglehold%20on%20institutions%20has%20shown%20in%20the%20decay%20at%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20internal%20watchdog%3A%20the%20CAG%20has%20stopped%20functioning%20effectively.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20CAG%20reports%20relating%20to%20Union%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments%20came%20down%20from%2055%20in%202015%20to%2014%20in%202020%2C%20a%20fall%20of%2075%25.%20The%20fall%20was%20sequential%3A%20going%20from%2055%20to%2042%2C%2045%2C%2023%2C%2021%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDefence%20audit%20reports%20went%20from%20seven%20in%202017%20to%20zero%20in%202020.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20body%20that%20had%20done%20much%20to%20undo%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20through%20its%20several%20strong%20reports%2C%20including%20on%20the%202G%20auction%2C%20coal%20block%20auction%2C%20and%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20on%20this%20front%20in%20recent%20times%3F%20Where%20people%20inside%20it%20attempt%20to%20make%20it%20function%20independently%2C%20they%20are%20punished.%20A%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20parliament%2C%2012%20CAG%20reports%20were%20presented%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20representatives.%20Days%20later%2C%20CAG%20officers%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20audits%20that%20revealed%20corruption%20were%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20transferred%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%5C%22%3EDattaprasad%20Suryakant%20Shirsat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20performance%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana.%20He%20had%20audited%20964%20hospitals%20in%20161%20districts%20of%20all%2028%20states%2C%20and%20found%20that%20in%202.25%20lakh%20cases%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csurgery%E2%80%9D%20was%20shown%20to%20be%20later%20than%20the%20date%20of%20discharge.%20More%20than%201.79%20lakh%20such%20cases%20were%20found%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20for%20which%20the%20claimed%20amount%20was%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore.%20A%20web%20portal%2C%20which%20broke%20this%20story%2C%20reported%20that%20lakhs%20of%20claims%20continued%20to%20be%20made%20for%20people%20who%20were%20deceased.%20The%20audit%20also%20found%201.57%20lakh%20instances%20of%20duplicated%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3ETreatment%20for%20the%20Dead%2C%20Discharge%20Before%20Surgery%20and%20the%20Many%20Problems%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAtoorva%20Sinha%2C%20who%20had%20audited%20highway%20projects%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1057421%2Fcag-transfers-officers-involved-in-audit-reports-alleging-irregularities-in-central-schemes%5C%22%3Ewas%20transferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20report%20found%20overrun%20costs%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project.%20The%20report%20said%20a%20change%20to%20elevate%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20pushed-up%20costs%20to%20Rs%20250%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20as%20against%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%2018%20crore%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20tries%20to%20raise%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20is%20not%20able%20to%20get%20the%20government%20to%20accept%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20much%20less%20to%20take%20action.%20The%20media%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20holding%20the%20government%20to%20account.%20It%20is%20the%20Opposition%20and%20civil%20society%20who%20are%20the%20primary%20targets%20of%20their%20coverage.%20Readers%20might%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20how%20the%20CAG%20was%20subverted%20from%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-controversial-record-of-a-modi-aide-who-may-head-the-enforcement-directorate%5C%22%3EGirish%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20cadre%20officer%20who%20is%20so%20loyal%20to%20Mr%20Modi%20that%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20he%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.truthofgujarat.com%2Fgc-murmu-principal-secretary-narendra-modi-coaching-witnesses-subvert-truth%2F%5C%22%3Ecaught%20on%20tape%3C%2Fa%3E%20intimidating%20senior%20officials%20from%20testifying%20against%20his%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20DGP%20of%20Gujarat%20R.B.%20Sreekumar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20State%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20from%20April%209%2C%202002%20to%20September%2017%2C%202002%2C%20in%20an%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20probing%20the%20Godhra%20riots%2C%20said%20that%20Mr%20Murmu%20%E2%80%9Ctutored%2C%20intimidated%2C%20forced%20and%20pressured%E2%80%9D%20him%20to%20depose%20in%20favour%20of%20Mr%20Modi.%20Mr%20Murmu%20was%20then%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sreekumar%20named%20another%20bureaucrat%20who%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20and%20said%20he%20was%20told%20not%20to%20give%20his%20deposition%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20names%20would%20be%20opened%20up%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20summoning%20for%20cross-examination%E2%80%A6%20I%20was%20also%20threatened%20that%20if%20I%20gave%20a%20statement%20contrary%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20interests%2C%20I%20will%20be%20declared%20a%20hostile%20witness%20and%20dealt%20with%20suitably%20later.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20would%20depose%20before%20the%20commission%20as%20per%20the%20statutory%20requirements%20and%20will%20not%20suppress%20the%20truth%2C%20because%20that%20would%20be%20an%20act%20of%20perjury%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Murmu%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cauthorised%20and%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20tutoring%20and%20briefing%20government%20officials%20deposing%20before%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20by%20the%20highest%20authorities%20of%20the%20government%20and%20home%20department%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20a%20posture%20by%20Shri%20Murmu%20is%20possible%20only%20if%20he%20has%20the%20specific%20support%20and%20clearance%20from%20the%20higher%20authorities%20in%20the%20government%3A%20the%20hon%E2%80%99ble%20home%20minister%2Fthe%20hon%E2%80%99ble%20chief%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20made%20him%20the%20governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20then%20the%20CAG.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpmindia.gov.in%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fpmindia.gov.in%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697559938531000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3G8OPeI_Vrf2ug_i9JL1_z%5C%22%3Epmindia.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20a%20section%20on%20transparency%20which%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20firmly%20believes%20that%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20are%20the%20two%20cornerstones%20of%20any%20pro-people%20government%E2%80%A6%20Transparency%20and%20accountability%20not%20only%20connect%20the%20people%20closer%20to%20the%20government%20but%20also%20make%20them%20an%20equal%20and%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20decision-making%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hard%20to%20reconcile%20these%20words%20with%20the%20actual%20actions%20of%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20on%20vital%20issues%20where%20opacity%20was%20preferred%20and%20promoted.%20This%20entire%20section%2C%20headlined%20%E2%80%9CQuest%20for%20transparency%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20site%2C%20has%20only%20184%20words%20and%20reads%20as%20if%20they%20were%20strung%20together%20by%20someone%20with%20little%20intellectual%20capacity%3A%20%E2%80%9CRules%20and%20policies%20were%20not%20framed%20in%20AC%20chambers%20but%20among%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDraft%20policies%20were%20put%20online%20for%20people%20to%20give%20their%20feedback%20and%20suggestions%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20is%20apparently%20an%20instance%20of%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20Mr%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20resolve%20to%20transparency%20backed%20by%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20put%20this%20commitment%20to%20practice%20indicates%20an%20era%20of%20open%2C%20transparent%20and%20people-centric%20government%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20No%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20The%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%20have%20been%20as%20opaque%2C%20and%20in%20many%20ways%20even%20more%20so%2C%20as%20those%20of%20any%20government%20before%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697534134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03200823%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-8.07.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftransparency-in-modi-era-cags-working-shows-it-remains-opaque%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20hard%20to%20reconcile%20these%20words%20with%20the%20actual%20actions%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20on%20vital%20issues%20where%20opacity%20was%20promoted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftransparency-in-modi-era-cags-working-shows-it-remains-opaque%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20flight%20instructor%20who%20converted%20an%20old%20cargo%20plane%20into%20an%20Airbnb%20and%20home%20for%20my%20students.%20Here's%20how%20I%20did%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jon%20Kotwicki%20turned%20an%20airplane%20into%20a%20house%20which%20he%20now%20rents%20out%20on%20airbnb%20and%20uses%20for%20his%20flight%20students.%20.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528499d6561dd877e795c4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJon%20Kotwicki%20turned%20an%20airplane%20into%20a%20house%20which%20he%20now%20rents%20out%20on%20airbnb%20and%20uses%20for%20his%20flight%20students.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EJon%20Kotwicki%2C%20a%20flight%20instructor%20bought%20an%20airplane%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20house%20for%20his%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAfter%20buying%20the%20airplane%20he%20had%20to%20decide%20how%20he%20would%20get%20the%20117-foot-wide%20aircraft%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20furnished%20airplane%20sleeps%20six%20people%20and%20Jon%20is%20now%20putting%20a%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20plane's%20wing.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E32%3Cem%3E-year-old%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20flight%20instructor%20in%20Alaska%2C%20who%20turned%20an%20old%20cargo%20plane%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df68110328e6797fb63b2cb88172b1323712a9fb87625fb5c03469795fef61898%26postID%3D65284afc385cb39deade31b0%26postSlug%3Dhow-i-turned-old-airplane-into-a-two-bedroom-airbnb-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.airbnb.com%252Frooms%252F908681227751910215%253Fsource_impression_id%253Dp3_1696611974_TW5Ev8LV0w6JVyiB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20into%20an%20Airbnb%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20moved%20from%20Florida%20to%20Alaska.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20this%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20flight%20school%20where%20my%20students%20could%20go%20up%20in%20a%20small%20airplane%20and%20learn%20to%20fly.%20I%20had%20a%20big%20vision%20for%20it.%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20proper%20runway%20and%20cabins%20for%20them%20to%20live%20in%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stop%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20thinking%2C%20instead%20of%20cabins%2C%20what%20if%20my%20students%20could%20live%20in%20an%20airplane%3F%20I%20knew%20that%20would%20be%20much%20cooler.%20I%20also%20knew%20when%20my%20students%20weren't%20staying%20in%20it%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20Airbnb.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-instructor-alaska-cargo-planes-airbnb-school-accommodation-photos-2023-4%5C%22%3EMy%20airplane%20house%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20big%2C%20and%20overboard%2C%20but%20my%20ideas%20usually%20are.%20In%202022%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20Douglas%20DC-6%20from%201956%20which%20I%20now%20rent%20out%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652971186561dd877e7a31fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221041%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EBuying%20an%20airplane%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20an%20airplane%20to%20convert%20wasn't%20easy.%20Usually%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-air-force-recycles-planes-2012-7%5C%22%3E%20old%20airplanes%20are%20sold%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20scrap%20companies%20for%20recycling.%20They're%20then%20crushed%20into%20beer%20cans.%20I%20spent%20a%20good%20six%20months%20reaching%20out%20to%20these%20companies%20and%20calling%20everyone%20I%20knew%20before%20finally%20finding%20a%20plane%20available%20for%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20buying%20a%201956%20Douglas%20DC-6.%20It%20was%20originally%20used%20for%20hauling%20cargo%20and%20fuel%20around%20Alaska%2C%20and%20to%20me%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20perfect%20conversion.%20After%20I%20bought%20the%20plane%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20getting%20it%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETransporting%20an%20airplane%20that%20can't%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOld%20airplanes%20are%20fairly%20cheap%20to%20buy.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20plane%20I%20bought%20can%20sometimes%20be%20as%20low%20as%20%2410%2C000%20for%20parts%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000.%20Now%2C%20transporting%20an%20airplane%20can%20be%20expensive.%20Between%20buying%20and%20transporting%20the%20plane%2C%20it%20cost%20us%20just%20over%20%24100%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20then%20left%20with%20a%20104-foot-long%2C%20and%20117-foot-wide%20airplane%20to%20move.%20To%20move%20it%2C%20my%20girlfriend%2C%20buddy%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20Fairhaven%2C%20Alaska%2C%20where%20the%20plane%20was%20located%20and%20began%20to%20disassemble%20it.%20We%20spent%20four%20days%20taking%20the%20plane%20apart%20and%20it%20took%20us%20a%20good%2016%20hours%20each%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20unbolted%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20cut%20off%20the%20wings%20to%20make%20it%20smaller%20for%20transport.%20Then%20we%20used%20cranes%20and%20forklifts%20to%20place%20the%20plane%20parts%20onto%20separate%20trailers.%20One%20of%20our%20trailers%20was%2093%20feet%20long.%20We%20drove%20the%20trailers%20350%20miles%20to%20our%20property%20in%20Wasilla%2C%20Alaska.%20Then%20it%20was%20time%20to%20place%20it%20back%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f156561dd877e7a2dfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ETurning%20an%20airplane%20into%20a%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20started%20the%20conversion%20process%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20because%20the%20plane%20already%20had%20walls%20and%20was%20completely%20enclosed%20like%20a%20house.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20easy.%20It%20took%20me%20five%20months%20to%20finish%20the%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20a%20normal%20house%2C%20we%20were%20building%20in%20an%20aluminum%20tin%20can.%20This%20meant%20we%20needed%20to%20find%20different%20ways%20to%20insulate%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20manage%20the%20moisture%20and%20the%20airflow.%20We%20also%20needed%20to%20heat%20the%20plane.%20Here%20in%20Alaska%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20natural%20gas.%20Instead%2C%20we%20usually%20heat%20our%20homes%20with%20wood%20or%20oil.%20In%20our%20airplane%2C%20we%20have%20an%20oil%20boiler%20in%20the%20tail%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20plumbing%2C%20the%20plane%20has%20its%20own%20water%20supply%20and%20septic%20system.%20When%20building%20the%20bathroom%2C%20we%20didn't%20want%20our%20space%20to%20have%20an%20average%20airplane%20sink%2C%20where%20you%20get%20only%20a%20trickle%20of%20water.%20Instead%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20the%20plane%20got%20its%20own%20pressure%20tank%20allowing%20our%20guests%20to%20take%20normal%20showers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversion%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20throwing%20away%20wasted%20materials%2C%20and%20rebuilding.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20hard%20process%2C%20but%20our%20plane%20came%20out%20better%20than%20I%20ever%20could%20have%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221425%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20airplane%20conversion%20has%20two%20bedrooms.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296fd06561dd877e7a2f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221069%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20airplane%20conversion%20has%20two%20bedrooms.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20airplane%20sleeps%20six%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20has%20a%20master%20bedroom%20with%20a%20king%20size%20bed%20and%20a%20guest%20room%20with%20a%20queen%20size%20bed.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20sofa%20bed%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20allowing%20the%20plane%20to%20sleep%20six%20people.%20Since%20it's%20an%20airplane%2C%20the%20rooms%20are%20narrow%20and%20they%20measure%20about%20nine%20feet%20wide.%20In%20comparison%2C%20an%20average%20room%20might%20be%20about%2012%20feet.%20There's%20also%20a%20bathroom%20with%20a%20fully%20tiled%20shower%20and%20a%20toilet.%20As%20for%20the%20kitchen%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20regular%20sink%2C%20refrigerator%2C%20freezer%2C%20a%20little%20toaster%20oven%2C%20microwave%2C%20and%20all%20of%20your%20basics%20for%20cooking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221423%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f6d6561dd877e7a2e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20now%20rent%20out%20the%20airplane%20house%20on%20Airbnb%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20originally%20made%20the%20airplane%20house%20for%20my%20students%2C%20but%20I%20also%20started%20renting%20it%20out%20on%20Airbnb%20in%20September%20starting%20at%20%24200%20a%20night.%20It%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%24700%20a%20night%20based%20on%20the%20season.%20Students%20travel%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20for%20their%20training%20with%20us%20and%20they%20need%20accommodation%2C%20so%20we%20provide%20it%20here%20on%20site.%20The%20accommodation%20is%20included%20in%20their%20training%20package.%20Either%20way%2C%20when%20people%20pull%20up%20to%20the%20Airplane%20house%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20love%20seeing%20their%20reactions.%20They're%20always%20so%20blown%20away%20by%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20here%2C%20you%20first%20drive%20down%20one%20long%20runway.%20Then%2C%20as%20you%20come%20out%20from%20around%20the%20trees%2C%C2%A0%20you%20see%20the%20giant%20airplane%20house.%20My%20favorite%20reaction%20was%20when%20a%20couple%20brought%20their%20two%20kids.%20They%20were%20little%20girls%2C%20approximately%20ages%20four%20and%20six%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20the%20biggest%20surprise%20to%20them.%20They%20were%20so%20excited.%20They%20ran%20up%20and%20down%20the%20entire%20airplane%2C%20full%20sprint%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20from%20the%20cockpit%20to%20the%20master%20bedroom.%20To%20me%2C%20those%20reactions%20are%20the%20best%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f156561dd877e7a2dfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20I'll%20soon%20be%20putting%20a%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20wing%20tip.%20I'm%20waiting%20for%20spring%20to%20do%20that%20project.%20I%20figure%20no%20one%20will%20want%20to%20use%20it%20in%20the%20winter%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20it%20gets%2020%20degrees%20below%20zero%20here.%20Once%20the%20hot%20tub%20is%20done%2C%20I%20know%20it%20will%20be%20a%20big%20attraction%20for%20those%20who%20rent%20from%20us.%20Finally%2C%20I%20am%20working%20on%20another%20airplane%20house%20too%2C%20that%20one%20will%20be%20a%20three%20bedroom%2C%20two%20bathroom%20and%20it%20will%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20sleep%20nine.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20fun%2C%20unique%20home%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Alyshia%20Hull%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aahull%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eahull%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-turned-old-airplane-into-a-two-bedroom-airbnb-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697533981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652849