l%20democracy%3F%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Britain%2C%20and%20the%20West%2C%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20know%20about%20and%20perhaps%20learn%20from%3F%20This%20fortnightly%20column%20helps%20forge%20the%20connections%20so%20essential%20in%20our%20globalising%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20immense%20tragedy%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%20It%20has%20devoured%20thousands%20of%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20lives%2C%20mostly%20civilians%3B%20and%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20claim%20many%20thousands%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20staring%20at%20an%20unfolding%20catastrophe%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yet%20collectively%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20nothing%20to%20stop%20it.%20That%20is%20a%20stain%20on%20us%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sophisticated%20military%20operation%20that%20Hamas%20launched%20earlier%20this%20month%20%E2%80%93%20firing%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20out%20of%20its%20Gaza%20stronghold%20north%20into%20Israel%20and%20sending%20thousands%20of%20its%20fighters%20over%20and%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20heavily%20armoured%20border%20fence%20%E2%80%93%20had%20the%20advantage%20of%20surprise.%20For%20the%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20this%20was%20largely%20a%20suicide%20mission.%20Their%20cruel%20goal%20was%20to%20take%20as%20many%20Israelis%20as%20they%20could%20down%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20aimed%20at%20soft%20civilian%20targets%2C%20massacring%20scores%20of%20youngsters%20at%20a%20music%20festival%20and%20slaughtering%20families%20in%20kibbutz%20settlements%2C%20agrarian%20communes%2C%20within%20easy%20reach.%20If%20reports%20from%20the%20scene%20are%20to%20be%20believed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20are%20%E2%80%93%20the%20attackers%20on%20occasion%20tortured%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20their%20victims.%20More%20than%20a%20hundred%20Israelis%20were%20taken%20back%20to%20Gaza%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20depraved%20and%20despicable%20and%20was%20called%20out%20not%20only%20by%20a%20furious%20(and%20perhaps%20humiliated)%20Israeli%20government%20but%20also%20in%20Washington%2C%20London%2C%20Paris%20and%20Kyiv%2C%20by%20administrations%20which%20are%20allies%20of%20Israel%20and%20strong%20advocates%20of%20a%20rules-based%20international%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%2C%20which%20is%20both%20Islamist%20and%20nationalist%2C%20seems%20to%20want%20to%20goad%20Israel%20into%20a%20brutal%20response.%20It%20turned%20to%20terror%20to%20provoke%20another%20kind%20of%20terror%2C%20blanket%20air%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20and%20an%20Israeli%20ground%20invasion%20accompanied%20by%20a%20profound%20humanitarian%20tragedy.%20The%20strategic%20aims%20is%20to%20infuriate%20Arab%20opinion%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20agony%20so%20that%20the%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%20the%20US%20has%20been%20brokering%2C%20is%20derailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20may%20also%20believe%20that%20this%20initial%20conflagration%20will%20spark%20a%20wider%20regional%20war%20to%20achieve%20the%20armed%20movement%E2%80%99s%20stated%20goal%3A%20the%20eradication%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20than%2020%20million%20Jews%20worldwide%2C%20of%20which%20about%20seven%20million%20live%20in%20Israel.%20They%20have%2C%20for%20centuries%2C%20faced%20poisonous%20antisemitism.%20Among%20the%20Israeli%20families%20struck%20in%20recent%20days%20are%20many%20which%2C%20two%20or%20three%20generations%20ago%2C%20suffered%20in%20the%20greatest%20infamy%20of%20the%20modern%20world%3A%20the%20Holocaust.%20About%206%20million%20European%20Jews%20were%20slaughtered%20in%20the%20industrial-scale%20genocide%20pursued%20by%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20generations%20earlier%2C%20many%20of%20their%20forebears%20fled%20from%20the%20Russian%20Empire%20in%20the%20face%20of%20ferocious%20pogroms%2C%20officially-sanctioned%20rioting%20and%20attacks%20on%20Jews.%20In%20all%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20near%20destitute%20Jews%20fled%20west%20in%20the%20thirty%20years%20before%201914%2C%20many%20making%20for%20America.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpalestine-solidarity-jantar-mantar-india%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98In%20Standing%20With%20Palestine%2C%20We%20Are%20Also%20Standing%20Up%20For%20Ourselves%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20killing%20of%20Israelis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0accompanied%20by%20the%20targeting%20of%20civilians%20including%20children%2C%20arouses%20the%20most%20terrible%20nightmares%20among%20so%20many%20Jewish%20households%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20state%20of%20Israel%20was%20set%20up%20in%201948%20because%20Jews%20were%20so%20evidently%20not%20safe%20in%20a%20state%20in%20which%20they%20were%20a%20minority.%20The%20answer%20was%20to%20have%20a%20homeland%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20of%20course%20an%20attempt%20to%20address%20one%20injustice%20created%20another.%20Palestinians%20regard%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Israel%20was%20created%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20cataclysm%2C%20because%20it%20involved%20the%20displacement%20of%20most%20Palestinian%20Arabs.%20The%20Palestinians%20are%20now%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20dispersed%20and%20have%20no%20real%20state%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaza%2C%20while%20nominally%20under%20Palestinian%20control%2C%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20Palestinian%20dispossession.%20In%20an%20area%20one-tenth%20the%20size%20of%20Goa%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20people%20live%20without%20any%20real%20economic%20base.%20They%20are%20hemmed%20in%20on%20all%20sides.%20Only%20a%20tiny%20number%20are%20allowed%20through%20the%20Israeli%20border%20to%20work.%20To%20the%20south%2C%20the%20Egyptians%20are%20even%20more%20restrictive%20about%20who%20can%20use%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20continues%20to%20occupy%20Palestinian%20land%20captured%20during%20a%20war%20half-a-century%20ago.%20And%20in%20defiance%20of%20international%20law%2C%20it%20is%20encouraging%20Israelis%20to%20settle%20there%20in%20fortified%20communities.%20For%20Palestinians%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20they%20are%20being%20squeezed%20again%20and%20again%20%E2%80%93%20their%20land%20isn%E2%80%99t%20safe%2C%20their%20homes%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe%2C%20their%20children%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20Palestinians%20have%20not%20been%20well%20or%20wisely%20led.%20The%20Palestinian%20Authority%20which%20has%20some%20control%20over%20parts%20of%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20is%20a%20byword%20for%20corruption%20and%20nepotism.%20In%20the%20pressure%20cooker%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Hamas%20has%20channelled%20the%20anger%20of%20local%20Palestinians%20towards%20the%20pursuit%20of%20violence%20and%20terror%20rather%20than%20improving%20lives%20and%20building%20diplomatic%20alliances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20is%20guaranteed%20the%20support%20of%20Iran%20and%20Syria%20however%20loathsome%20its%20acts.%20Israel%20knows%20that%20Washington%20will%20stand%20by%20it%20come%20what%20may.%20The%20United%20Nations%2C%20the%20one%20practical%20friend%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20through%20the%20decades%2C%20is%20able%20to%20do%20nothing%20but%20issue%20platitudes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20hardliners%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20profound%20suffering%20in%20their%20own%20community%20is%20seen%20as%20sufficient%20reason%20to%20inflict%20terrible%20suffering%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20moderate%2C%20consensus-minded%20voices%20%E2%80%93%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%93%20are%20once%20again%20being%20drowned%20out%20by%20the%20din%20of%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree-quarters%20of%20a%20century%20after%20Israel%20was%20created%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20loop%20tape%20of%20hatred%2C%20distrust%2C%20destruction%20and%20barbarity.%20Those%20of%20us%20who%20look%20on%20in%20horror%20have%20no%20useful%20way%20to%20help%20achieve%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%20is%20an%20honorary%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20Correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697533229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144837%2FF8Ujv0qWkAA5W3q.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three-quarters%20of%20a%20century%20after%20Israel%20was%20created%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20loop%20tape%20of%20hatred%2C%20distrust%2C%20destruction%20and%20barbarity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ft