0World%20Cup%20after%20failures%20in%201983%20and%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20anybody%20should%20talk%20about%20this.%20Secondly%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20captained%20in%201983%20and%201987%20and%20lost%20both%20times%20before%20winning%20on%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%201992.%20Any%20good%20player%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20as%20a%20captain%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Yousuf%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMainHoonSultan7%2Fstatus%2F1713887722966847717%5C%22%3ESamaa%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Babar)%20is%20the%20captain%20because%20he%20has%20the%20ability.%20He%20did%20not%20become%20the%20captain%20because%20he%20is%20related%20to%20the%20PCB%20chairman.%20He%20is%20a%20genuine%20skipper.%20So%20talking%20about%20him%20in%20this%20manner%20is%20a%20loss%20for%20Pakistan%20and%20for%20him%20as%20well%2C%20especially%20amid%20the%20immense%20pressure%20post%20that%20loss%20against%20India.%20I%20am%20shocked%20that%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20there%2C%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697529060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fqdj38ccg_babar-azam-and-wasim-akram_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshocked-that-wasim-akram-pakistan-great-mohammad-yousuf-on-shoaib-malik-questioning-babar-azams-captaincy-4487629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Wasim%20Akram%20in%20his%20company%2C%20Shoaib%20Malik%20suggested%20that%20Babar%20Azam%20should%20step%20down%20as%20Pakistan's%20captain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshocked-that-wasim-akram-pakistan-great-mohammad-yousuf-on-shoaib-malik-questioning-babar-azams-captaincy-4487629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshocked-that-wasim-akram-pakistan-great-mohammad-yousuf-on-shoaib-malik-questioning-babar-azams-captaincy-4487629%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshocked-that-wasim-akram-pakistan-great-mohammad-yousuf-on-shoaib-malik-questioning-babar-azams-captaincy-4487629%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20Movie%20'Razakar%20%E2%80%93%20Silent%20Genocide%20of%20Hyderabad'%20Sets%20Out%20to%20Distort%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17131654%2FScreenshot-2023-10-17-at-1.16.23-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZk3yfhHTwJ8%5C%22%3Eteaser%20of%20%3Cem%3ERazakar%20%E2%80%93%20Silent%20Genocide%20of%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20movie%20purported%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20historic%20realities%20of%20Nizam%20rule%20in%20Telangana%20just%20before%20and%20after%20Indian%20independence%2C%20was%20released%20in%20September.%20The%20teaser%20claims%20that%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20Hyderabad%20an%20independent%20Islamic%20state%20and%20a%20silent%20genocide%20was%20committed%20on%20the%20Hindu%20population%20of%20Hyderabad%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20structure%2C%20nearly%20static%20since%20inception%2C%20was%20headed%20by%20the%20Nizam.%20Below%20him%20were%20the%20Muslim%20nobility%20in%20the%20court.%20Below%20them%20were%20a%20huge%20retinue%2C%20mostly%20Hindus%2C%20helping%20the%20Nizam%20in%20administering%20the%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%2053%20million%20acres%20of%20land%2C%2010%25%20was%20the%20fiefdom%20of%20the%20Nizam%2C%2030%25%20was%20with%20nobles%20and%20landlords%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20was%20under%20government%20land%20revenue.%20In%20addition%20to%20back-breaking%20taxes%2C%20all%20methods%20were%20used%20to%20exploit%20the%20peasantry.%20Accentuating%20these%20problems%20are%20the%20religious%20and%20linguist%20differences%20between%20the%20ruled%20and%20the%20ruler%20%E2%80%93%20acutely%20felt%20by%20the%20urban%20elite.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%20while%20the%20regime%20was%20patently%20pro-Muslim%2C%20the%20rural%20set%20up%20was%20bolstered%20by%20Hindu%20upper%20castes%20thus%20it%20was%20not%20an%20Islamic%20theocratic%20state.%20Within%20the%20feudal%20set%20up%20that%20the%20Nizam%20was%20presiding%20over%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Nizam%20was%20syncretic%20as%20he%20gave%20grants%20to%20temples%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20and%20for%20promoting%20works%20not%20limited%20to%20Islam.%20This%20was%20further%20strengthened%20as%20the%20Nizam%20banned%20cow%20slaughter%20in%20public%20places%20in%201923.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%201946%2C%20with%20the%20imminent%20departure%20of%20the%20British%2C%20chaos%20set%20in%20and%20Hyderabad%20became%20a%20power%20keg.%20The%20Nizam%20wanted%20to%20cling%20to%20power%2C%20come%20what%20may.%20As%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20army%20was%20weak%20and%20police%20inadequate%20and%20corrupt%2C%20he%20encouraged%20a%20Muslim%20extremist%20organisation%2C%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(MIM).%20Under%20the%20militant%20presidentship%20of%20Kasim%20Razvi%2C%20its%20militia%20swelled%20to%20around%20200%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20propped%20by%20the%20inflow%20of%20Muslims%20from%20within%20and%20outside%20Hyderabad%20state.%20They%20were%20joined%20by%20militia%20of%20the%20rural%20gentry%2C%20who%20were%20mostly%20Hindu%2C%20and%20some%20lower%20caste%20Hindus%20badly%20impacted%20by%20caste%20and%20economic%20oppression.%20Thus%20while%20it%20was%20a%20predominantly%20Muslim%20force%2C%20it%20had%20some%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20were%20active%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20in%20Marathi-%20and%20Kannada-speaking%20areas.%20They%20trained%20cadre%20within%20the%20state%20and%20also%20outside%2C%20and%20focused%20narrowly%20on%20%3Cem%3Eshuddi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(religious%20reconversion)%20and%20Hindu%20rights.%20As%20per%20Padmaja%20Naidu%2C%20as%20quoted%20in%20Lucien%20D%20Benichou%E2%80%99s%20%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EFrom%20Autocracy%20To%20Integration%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fspan%3Ecommunal%20tensions%20arose%20owing%20to%20the%20competitive%20conversions%20by%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20Muslim%20organisations.%20She%20further%20says%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20a%20divided%20house%2C%20with%20most%20conservatives%20supporting%20communal%20elements.%20Sporadic%20satyagraha%20calls%20from%20the%20Congress%20also%20unnerved%20the%20Nizam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20parallel%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Maha%20Sabha%20and%20Communist%20led%20resistance%20of%20common%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%20of%20Telangana%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Warangal%2C%20Nalgonda%20and%20Khammam.%20By%20September%201948%2C%20in%20about%203%2C000%20villages%20landlords%20were%20driven%20out%20and%20self%20rule%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20poor%20and%20around%2010%20lakh%20acres%20of%20land%20distributed%20to%20people.%20However%2C%20no%20such%20resistance%20movements%20were%20noticed%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20and%20Marathwada%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EK.%20M.%20Munshi%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20End%20of%20an%20Era%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20writes%20that%20between%20October%201947%20and%20April%201948%2C%20Razakars%20(a%20paramilitary%20force)%20committed%20260%20events%20of%20brutality%20but%20does%20not%20elaborate%20further.%20A%20white%20paper%20published%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%201948%20describes%2053%20events%20of%20Razakar%20atrocities%20in%20four%20districts%20of%20Marathwada.%20As%20per%20author%E2%80%99s%20assessment%2C%20in%20the%2053%20events%20around%20200%20deaths%20occurred%2C%20probably%2020%20rapes%20were%20committed%20(may%20be%20an%20underestimate%20as%20rapes%20are%20not%20stated%20easily)%2C%20and%20around%2050%20incidents%20of%20loot%20happened%20of%20which%20around%2030%20were%20against%20the%20rich%20like%20moneylenders%2C%20business%20people%20or%20village%20heads.%20If%20one%20extends%20the%20same%20proportion%20to%20the%20260%20events%2C%20probable%20deaths%20would%20be%20around%20980.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Fop-ed%2Fusing-cinema-to-stoke-communal-tensions%2Farticle67307190.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ecites%20one%20report%20to%20say%20Razakars%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20880%20people%20and%20the%20rape%20of%20about%201%2C125%20women%20before%20August%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20areas%20under%20the%20control%20of%20communists%20was%20entirely%20different%2C%20as%20people%20resisted%20and%20replied%20to%20the%20Razakars%20in%20the%20same%20coin.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%202%2C000%20communist%20militants%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%2C%20but%20killed%20a%20similar%20number%20in%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20events%2C%20originally%20written%20about%20by%20Munshi%20and%20reported%20in%20various%20other%20fora%2C%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%20to%20understand%20the%20nature%20of%20Razakar%20atrocities.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20Shoebullah%20Khan%2C%20a%20journalist.%20His%20only%20crime%20was%20he%20was%20advocating%20for%20the%20merger%20of%20Hyderabad%20into%20India.%20His%20murder%20showed%20that%20all%20opponents%20were%20killed%2C%20religious%20affiliation%20did%20not%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20more%20brutal%20event%20was%20the%20murder%20of%20200%20people%20in%20Gorata%20B%20village%20in%20Basavakalyan%20in%20Karnataka.%20According%20to%20Munshi%2C%20this%20was%20the%20chain%20of%20events%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20January%2029%2C%20the%20Minister%20Venkatarao%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Ittehad%20Harijans%2C%20made%20a%20vicious%20attack%20in%20an%20open%20conference%20on%20the%20Brahmans%2C%20Banias%20and%20Lingayats%20%E2%80%A6He%20declared%20that%20the%20Lingayats%20were%20the%20arch%20criminals%20%E2%80%A6miseries%20of%20the%20depressed%20classes%20and%20he%20therefore%20exhorted%20his%20people%20to%20exterminate%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Munshi%20indicates%20that%20Muslims%20did%20attack%2C%20but%20had%20some%20backing%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20event%20was%20in%20Bairanpalli%20village%20in%20Telangana%20where%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20attacks%20of%20Razakars%20and%20police%20to%20reinstate%20the%20local%20landlords%20were%20rebuffed%20by%20the%20villagers.%20Finally%2C%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20military%20was%20deployed%20leading%20to%20the%20death%20of%2088%20people.%20Hindus%20were%20killed%20to%20bring%20back%20Hindu%20landlords%20%E2%80%93%20not%20a%20communal%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20above%2C%20it%20can%20be%20seen%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20religion%20there%20were%20other%20proximate%20causes%20for%20violence.%20Reinstatement%20of%20the%20local%20landlords%20is%20the%20most%20important%20reason%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20and%20immediately%20after%20the%20police%20action%2C%20around%2025%2C000-30%2C000%20Muslims%20were%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Sundarlal%20committee.%20It%20also%20noted%20that%20at%20many%20places%2C%20army%20and%20police%20personnel%20took%20active%20part%20in%20perpetuating%20the%20violence.%20The%20report%20also%20states%20that%20violence%20was%20also%20perpetuated%20by%20men%20from%20a%20communal%20organisation%20from%20Solapur.%20Between%201948%20and%20%E2%80%9951%2C%202%2C000%20communists%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20with%20the%20help%20of%20local%20landlords%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20reinstating%20them%20in%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20narrative%20affirms%20there%20was%20violence%20and%20mayhem%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20a%20genocide%20of%20a%20particular%20religious%20community.%20Till%201947%2C%20Asaf%20Jahis%20(the%20ruling%20dynasty)%20not%20only%20did%20not%20show%20any%20streak%20of%20religious%20extremism%2C%20but%20even%20co-opted%20the%20Hindu%20rural%20gentry%20to%20exploit%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20meek.%20Events%20after%201947%20also%20show%20how%20the%20Razakars%2C%20while%20using%20religious%20slogans%20to%20mobilise%2C%20were%20undertaking%20a%20secular%20activity%20of%20amassing%20wealth%20or%20reinstating%20the%20Hindu%20landlords%20to%20their%20lands.%20Thus%20a%20Hindu%20genocide%20was%20never%20the%20intention%20nor%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20the%20rhetoric%20was%20communal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20an%20Islamic%20republic%2C%20Asaf%20Jahis%20never%20showed%20this%20intent%20in%20their%20225%20years%20of%20rule.%20They%20always%20had%20fair-weather%20friends%20from%20all%20faiths.%20Even%20in%201947%2C%20the%20Nizam%20was%20more%20worried%20about%20his%20kingdom%20and%20not%20what%20happens%20to%20Islam%20or%20to%20other%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20film%20title%20%3Cem%3ERazakar%20%E2%80%93%20Silent%20Genocide%20of%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20assertions%20in%20the%20teaser%20are%20a%20distortion%20of%20history.%20But%20in%20these%20days%20of%20lies%20and%20half-truths%2C%20facts%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20As%20a%20Telugu%20saying%20goes%2C%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattempt%20to%20collect%20money%20on%20dead%20bodies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Ravibabu%20is%20a%20retired%20civil%20servant%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Anekdhara%20%E2%80%93%20a%20public%20policy%20forum.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697528903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17131654%2FScreenshot-2023-10-17-at-1.16.23-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fhow-the-movie-razakar-silent-genocide-of-hyderabad-sets-out-to-distort-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3