%26quot%3B...%20the%20steel%20industry%20and%20cement%20industry...%20whenever%20they%20get%20the%20chance%2C%20they%20make%20the%20cartel%20and%20increase%20the%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20rating%20of%20companies%20who%20make%20DPRs%20is%20a%20big%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20preparation%20of%20DPRs%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20for%20NHAI...%20there%20is%20no%20perfect%20DPR%20anywhere%20in%20any%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20frank%20views%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20making%20DPR%2C%20they%20(companies%20engaged%20in%20DPR%20making)%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20new%20technology%2C%20new%20innovation%2C%20new%20research%20and%20even%20the%20standard%20of%20DPRs%20are%20so%20low%20that%20everywhere%20(there%20is)%20additional%20scope%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20high%20logistics%20costs%20in%20India%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20India%2C%20logistics%20cost%20is%2014-16%20per%20cent%2C%20compared%20to%208-10%20per%20cent%20in%20China.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697528580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2F84m6r7ug_highway-generic-night-shot_625x300_30_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitin-gadkari-reveals-how-big-players-form-cartels-to-hamper-road-projects-4488358%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20is%20facing%20difficulties%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20detailed%20project%20reports%2C%20as%20companies%20concerned%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20new%20technology%2C%20union%20minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20said%20today.%22%2C%22autho