raph-0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20rupee%20closed%20at%20a%20lifetime%20low%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%20on%20Monday%20(October%2016)%20due%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20crude%20oil%20prices%20and%20weakening%20Asian%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EThe%20rupee%20closed%20at%2083.2775%20against%20the%20dollar%2C%20barely%20changed%20from%20its%20previous%20close%2C%20which%20had%20marked%20a%20record%20low.%20The%20currency%20hit%20its%20previous%20record%20closing%20low%20of%2083.2675%20on%20September%2018%2C%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EThe%20dollar%20index%20remained%20steady%2C%20and%20Asian%20currencies%2C%20especially%20the%20Korean%20won%2C%20showed%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EA%20foreign%20exchange%20trader%20at%20a%20foreign%20bank%20told%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20rupee%20is%20%E2%80%9Cslowly%20weakening%20but%20remains%20sticky%20as%20usual%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20because%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20likely%20interventions%20that%20have%20limited%20the%20currency%E2%80%99s%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20supplied%20US%20dollars%20during%20trading%20sessions.%20State-run%20banks%20also%20sold%20US%20dollars%2C%20likely%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20RBI%20when%20the%20rupee%20reached%20its%20weakest%20level%20during%20the%20day.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-6%5C%22%3ENear%20the%20end%20of%20the%20session%20when%20the%20rupee%20fell%20to%2083.28%2C%20its%20weakest%20level%20during%20the%20day%2C%20state-run%20banks%20were%20seen%20selling%20US%20dollars%20again%2C%20likely%20on%20behalf%20of%20RBI%2C%20four%20traders%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUncertainty%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20higher%20energy%20prices%20will%20see%20investors%20continue%20to%20back%20the%20energy-independent%20dollar%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%E2%80%9D%20ING%20Bank%20said%20in%20a%20note%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20RBI%20is%20likely%20to%20keep%20defending%20the%2083.30%20level%20on%20the%20rupee%20but%2083.40%20would%20be%20the%20next%20support%20if%20that%20level%20is%20breached%2C%20Sajal%20Gupta%2C%20head%20of%20forex%20and%20commodities%20at%20Nuvama%20Wealth%20Management%E2%80%99s%20institutional%20desk%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20Reuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697520672000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmacro%2Frupee-closed-at-a-lifetime-low-on-monday-amid-worries-over-oil-prices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rupee%20closed%20at%2083.2775%20against%20the%20dollar%2C%20barely%20changed%20from%20its%20previous%20close%2C%20which%20had%20marked%20a%20record%20low.%20The%20currency%20hit%20its%20previous%20record%20closing%20low%20of%2083.2675%20on%20September%2018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmacro%2Frupee-closed-at-a-lifetime-low-on-monday-amid-worries-over-oil-prices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maruti%20to%20pay%20%241.54%20billion%20in%20stock%20to%20Suzuki%20Motor%20for%20local%20plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697520292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696788646-0695.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmaruti-to-issue-1-2-million-shares-to-suzuki-motor-to-buy-local-plant-12310170