n%20of%20the%20party%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Csecular%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20the%20power%2C%20as%20the%20state%20president%2C%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2022%2C%20the%20second-in-command%20of%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20met%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20BJP%20President%20J.P.%20Nadda%20in%20Delhi%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjanata-dal-secular-joins-the-national-democratic-alliance%5C%22%3Eformalised%20the%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20then%2C%20JD(S)%20party%20units%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-unit-of-jds-rejects-deve-gowdas-decision-to-join-hands-with-bjp-to-continue-its-alliance-with-left-front%2Farticle67392475.ece%5C%22%3EKerala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%20conveyed%20their%20displeasure%20over%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20even%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20JD(S)%20presence%20outside%20Karnataka%20is%20limited%2C%20the%20latest%20statement%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20party%20unit%20president%20assumes%20significance%20given%20that%20it%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf.%20Ibrahim%E2%80%99s%20divergent%20views%20to%20that%20of%20the%20leadership%20indicate%20a%20possible%20split%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20decision%20is%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20will%20not%20go%20with%20the%20NDA.%20The%20second%20decision%20was%20a%20request%20to%20Deve%20Gowda%20that%20he%20should%20not%20give%20his%20consent%20to%20this%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20told%20reporters%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20some%20party%20leaders%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fjds-not-joining-nda-karnataka-party-chief-contradicts-deve-gowda-hints-at-split-2728792%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Karnataka%2C%20however%2C%20we%20still%20have%20affection%20for%20you.%20You%20are%20a%20father%20figure.%20We%20will%20tell%20him%20(Gowda)%20that%20we%20should%20not%20have%20any%20relation%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20be%20forming%20a%20core%20committee%2C%20which%20will%20meet%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20convey%20the%20decision%20taken%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20specifically%20if%20Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20his%20views%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20state%20president.%20I%20have%20to%20decide%20about%20my%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20I%20will%20take.%20Already%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20not%20go%20with%20the%20BJP.%20What%20else%20is%20there%20more%20than%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20he%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIf%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20the%20BJP%20then%20let%20them%20go%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20asking%20them%20(Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy)%20not%20to%20go.%20If%20they%20go%20then%20we%20cannot%20bind%20them.%20Regarding%20(JD-S)%20MLAs%2C%20please%20wait%20and%20see%20who%2C%20how%20many%2C%20and%20where%20these%20MLAs%20will%20take%20a%20decision.%20We%20will%20intimate%20you%20when%20the%20time%20comes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20JD(S)%20state%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIbrahim%20claimed%20that%20several%20party%20MLAs%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20him%20and%20he%20would%20soon%20hold%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20them.%20He%20declined%20to%20spell%20out%20the%20names%20of%20MLAs%20whom%20he%20claimed%20to%20be%20in%20touch%20with%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20exert%20pressure%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697469845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22173251%2Fimag