in%20a%20reputed%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6.%20Candidates%20who%20have%20submitted%20their%20PhD%20theses%20may%20also%20apply%20for%20the%20post%20of%20RA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20note%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Interested%20candidates%20can%20fill%20out%20the%20application%20form%20in%20the%20prescribed%20format%20and%20send%20it%20to%20The%20Director%2C%20Armament%20Research%20and%20Development%20Establishment%20(ARDE)%2C%20Armament%20Post%2C%20Pashan%2C%20PUNE-%20411%20021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20Shortlisted%20candidates%20will%20be%20called%20out%20for%20an%20interview%20before%20they%20are%20awarded%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20The%20interview%20test%20will%20be%20conducted%20on%201%20December%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20For%20the%20post%20of%20JRF%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20walk-in-interview%20held%20at%20NSTL%2C%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20on%2021%20November%20and%2023%20December%2C%202023%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudycafe.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDRDO-Recruitment-2023-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20document%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Selected%20candidates%20will%20be%20given%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2037%2C000%20for%20Junior%20Research%20Fellow%20and%20Rs%2067%2C000%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Research%20Associate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697464174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20is%20inviting%20applicants%20for%20multiple%20research-based%20job%20openings%20in%20Pune%20and%20Visakhapatnam.%20Know%20more%20to%20apply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22ca