rnment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%5C%22%3Ebecause%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98unhappy%20with%20data%20sets%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20NFHS-5.%20His%20suspension%20was%20formally%20revoked%20last%20week%2C%20only%20for%20his%20resignation%20to%20be%20accepted%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECopies%20of%20the%20orders%20revoking%20his%20suspension%20and%20accepting%20the%20resignation%20are%20available%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20competent%20authority%2C%20on%20subsequent%20review%2C%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20in%20view%20of%20material%20changes%20in%20the%20circumstances%2C%20the%20suspension%20of%20Prof.%20K.%20S.%20James%20may%20not%20be%20extended%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%20dated%20October%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20July%2C%20following%20his%20suspension%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20released%20an%20unsigned%20and%20undated%20note%20to%20the%20media%20which%20claimed%20that%20a%20fact-finding%20committee%20found%20merit%2C%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%2011%20out%20of%2035%20complaints%20allegedly%20received%20against%20James.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20irregularities%20were%20mainly%20regarding%20%5Bthe%5D%20lapses%20observed%20in%20certain%20appointments%2C%20recruitments%20of%20faculty%2C%20Reservation%20Roasters%2C%20Dead%20Stock%20registers%2C%20etc.%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20the%20note%2C%20the%20ministry%20did%20not%20clarify%20for%20what%20charges%20the%20committee%20found%20prima%20facie%20merit%20or%20when%20the%20complaints%20against%20James%20were%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhealth-ministry-government-note-ks-james-iips-data-nfhs%5C%22%3EGovt%20Note%20Cites%20%E2%80%98Charges%E2%80%99%20Against%20IIPS%20Head%2C%20Insiders%20Say%20He%20Was%20Already%20Facing%20Flak%20For%20%E2%80%98Unflattering%E2%80%99%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20committee%20was%20never%20made%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20unnamed%20source%2C%20purportedly%20from%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fchina-webinar-leaking-research-grounds-cited-by-govt-for-suspending-head-of-institute-behind-nfhs%2F1696266%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20James%20had%20participated%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9CChina-based%20webinar%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20apparently%20raised%20eyebrows%20within%20the%20ministry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20without%20clarifying%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20inquiry%20initiated%20after%20his%20suspension%2C%20James%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20has%20been%20revoked.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20seeking%20its%20response.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reliably%20learnt%20that%20once%20James%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20was%20revoked%20on%20October%2011%2C%20he%20was%20reinstated%20formally.%20Within%20an%20hour%20of%20his%20reinstatement%2C%20his%20resignation%2C%20tendered%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20grounds%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20accepted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20source%20at%20the%20institute%20confirmed%20that%20to%20date%2C%20nobody%20at%20IIPS%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20is%20aware%20what%20were%20the%2011%20charges%20that%20were%20found%20prima%20facie%20true%20in%20the%20preliminary%20report%20of%20the%20ministry%20and%20led%20to%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20suspension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20office%20was%20not%20made%20aware%20of%20those%20allegations%2C%20there%20was%20no%20response%20to%20them.%20However%2C%20James%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20continued%20to%20remain%20in%20place%20until%20he%20tendered%20his%20resignation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20James%20for%20comment%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20going%20into%20the%20details%20about%20the%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20his%20suspension%2C%20its%20revocation%20and%20his%20resignation.%20However%2C%20he%20confirmed%20that%20he%20had%20resigned%20in%20August.%20Currently%2C%20he%20has%20accepted%20the%20position%20of%20a%20short-term%20visiting%20scholar%20at%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Applied%20Systems%20Analysis%2C%20Vienna.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30144931%2FUntitled-design-22-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30144931%2FUntitled-design-22-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30144931%2FUntitled-design-22-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30144931%2FUntitled-design-22-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665872%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnion%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20and%20K.S.%20James.%20In%20the%20background%20are%20students%20and%20faculty%20at%20the%202022%20convocation%20of%20IIPS.%20Photos%3A%20Official%20Twitter%20and%20www.iipsindia.ac.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98India%E2%80%99s%20loss%2C%20IIPS%E2%80%99s%20loss%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Espoke%20to%20two%20IIPS%20faculty%20members%20%E2%80%93%20one%20professor%20and%20another%20associate%20professor%20%E2%80%93%20at%20two%20departments.%20They%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20angry%20but%20we%20are%20helpless%20%5Babout%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20resignation%5D.%20This%20has%20never%20happened%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20faculty%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20resist%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20faculty%20member%20confirmed%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20earlier%20report%20about%20discomfort%20within%20the%20government%20about%20figures%20on%20anaemia%20in%20NFHS-5%2C%20which%20was%20released%20under%20James%E2%80%99s%20watch.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20some%20pressure%E2%80%A6%20but%20ultimately%20it%20%5BNFHS-5%20data%5D%20was%20published%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20held%20an%20important%20position%20in%20the%20committee%20which%20finally%20approves%20the%20data%20before%20publication%20and%20%5Btherefore%5D%20he%20could%20carry%20forward%20the%20%5Bfinal%5D%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20added.%20The%20committee%20consists%20of%20several%20independent%20domain%20experts%20outside%20the%20institute.%20The%20final%20stamp%20of%20approval%2C%20before%20the%20data%20is%20made%20publicly%20available%2C%20though%20comes%20from%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20showed%20that%20anaemia%20had%20increased%20in%20the%20NFHS-5%20period%20(2019-21)%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20round%2C%20NFHS-4.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20NFHS-5%20also%20revealed%20that%20India%20was%20not%20open%20defecation-free%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20repeatedly%20made%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20several%20Union%20ministers.%20The%20survey%20showed%20that%20in%20no%20state%20or%20Union%20Territory%20(UT)%2C%20except%20Lakshadweep%2C%20100%25%20of%20the%20population%20have%20access%20to%20toilet%20facilities.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20NFHS-5%20data%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98success%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Ujjwala%20scheme%20to%20encourage%20LPG%20as%20cooking%20fuel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20professor%20said%20there%20are%20already%20talks%20ongoing%20of%20some%20%E2%80%98uncomfortable%20indicators%E2%80%99%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20ongoing%20data%20collection%20process%20for%20NFHS-6.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20associate%20professor%20feared%20that%20the%20credibility%20of%20NFHS-6%20might%20go%20for%20a%20toss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20colleagues%20working%20on%20NFHS-6%20are%20in%20a%20tight%20spot.%20Some%20of%20them%20do%20worry%20about%20the%20%5Bdata%20for%5D%20indicators%20%5Bthat%20they%20are%20collecting%20now%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20associate%20professor%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENFHS%20is%20a%20large-scale%20exercise%20that%20spans%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20that%20IIPS%20undertakes%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry.%20It%20provides%20data%20on%20important%20indicators%20not%20just%20related%20to%20health%20but%20also%20other%20aspects%20of%20human%20development%20which%20governments%20have%20sought%20to%20improve%20through%20several%20targeted%20schemes.%20The%20NFHS%20data%20helps%20understand%20the%20ground%20impact%20of%20those%20schemes%20and%20is%20heavily%20referenced%20in%20academic%20and%20policy-making%20circles%20at%20both%20national%20and%20state%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20faculty%20members%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20spillover%20effect%20on%20the%20institute%2C%20especially%20about%20various%20international%20collaborations%20that%20the%20IIPS%20could%20forge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20funding%20agencies%20will%20think%20twice%20about%20sanctioning%20projects%20because%20the%20message%20has%20gone%20out%20%5Bthat%20the%20director%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20for%20presenting%20accurate%20data%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20said.%20Asked%20to%20explain%20further%2C%20he%20said%20the%20institute%20does%20rigorous%20surveys%20not%20just%20for%20the%20government%20of%20India%20but%20also%20partners%20with%20agencies%20such%20as%20Unicef%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20associate%20professor%20said%20James%20was%20successful%20in%20launching%20joint%20courses%20with%20foreign%20universities.%20%E2%80%9CSeveral%20MoUs%20were%20signed%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20associate%20professor%20added.%20Both%20of%20them%20wondered%20if%20that%20momentum%20would%20continue%20anymore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20said%20the%20immediate%20fallout%20of%20James%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20the%20shifting%20of%20the%20venue%20for%20the%20sixth%20Asian%20Population%20Association%20Conference%20that%20will%20be%20held%20in%20November%20next%20year.%20It%20is%20a%20coveted%20conference%20in%20the%20field%20of%20demography%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20more%20than%20600%20experts%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20conference%20was%20to%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asianpa.org%2Fnews-activities%2Fapa-activities-and-announcements%2F650-the-first-announcement-of-the-6th-apa-conference-november-27-30%2C-2024.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Asian%2520Population%2520Association%2520(APA%2Cto%252030th%2520November%25202024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehosted%20by%20IIPS%20in%20Mumbai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20associate%20professor%20said%20that%20until%20early%20October%2C%20the%20hosting%20rights%20remained%20with%20IIPS%20but%20it%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20an%20institute%20in%20Kathmandu.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20immediately%20verify%20if%20the%20change%20of%20venue%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20ongoing%20developments%20at%20IIPS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697461225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28214547%2FUntitled-design-21-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-iips-director-resignation-nfhs-health-ministry%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20K.S.%20James's%20gone%2C%20International%20Institute%20of%20Population%20Sciences%20faculty%20say%20the%20credibility%20of%20upcoming%20NFHS%20rounds%20may%20go%20for%20a%20toss%20and%20the%20data%20may%20not%20be%20considered%20fully%20reliable.%20NFHS%20is%20a%20large-scale%20data%20collection%20exercise%20IIPS%20conducts%20for%20all%20states%2FUTs%20regarding%20various%20health%20and%20some%20development%20indicators%20and%20helps%20track%20the%20impact%20of%20targeted%20schemes%20launched%20to%20address%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-iips-director-resignation-nfhs-health-ministry%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Voice%20notes%20from%20Palestinians%20%7C%20What%20we%20know%20about%20the%20199%20hostages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697458680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F1600x900%2F2372310160349387007_