ould%20be%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERestoring%20such%20homes%20can%20be%20very%20expensive%20and%20time-consuming.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20resources%20are%20used%20to%20reconstruct%20or%20repair%20these%20homes%20such%20as%20mortar%20and%20it%20also%20causes%20a%20lot%20of%20wastage.%20LGSF%20technology%20is%20great%20in%20that%20respect%20as%20it%20gives%20the%20house%20a%20high%20strength-to-weight%20ratio%2C%20making%20them%20more%20resilient%20to%20forces%20such%20as%20earthquakes%2C%20hurricanes%2C%20and%20heavy%20winds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20people%20are%20sceptical%20about%20it%2C%20we%20have%20already%20made%20a%20few%20homes%20using%20the%20technology%20in%20Kerala%20and%20are%20soon%20planning%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpand%20to%20Karnataka%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Tamil%20Nadu%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Dr%20Jayakumar%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20Majid%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20beautiful%20home%20and%20the%20client%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20as%20cosy%20as%20it%20can%20be.%20The%20plot%20is%20on%20two%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ground%20level%20was%20utilised%20for%20parking%20space%20and%20the%20upper%20level%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20home.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20months%20for%20the%20home%20to%20complete.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20structure%20and%20planning%20were%20done%20in%20just%20a%20month%20and%20since%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20house%20was%20quite%20detailed%20it%20took%20us%20another%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20complete%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complete%20construction%20of%20the%20house%20cost%20Dr%20Jayakumar%20just%20about%20Rs%2080%20lakhs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStep-by-step%20guide%20to%20LGSF%20homes%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20way%20the%20technology%20works%2C%20Majid%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20step%20to%20building%20an%20LGSF%20home%20is%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20customer%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20structure.%20The%20architect%20then%20presents%20the%20preliminary%20sketching%20and%20designing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20design%20is%20done%2C%20it%20is%20moved%20to%20the%20structure%20team.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20team%20makes%20the%20drawings%20and%20finalises%20the%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20structure%20plan%20is%20ready%2C%20we%20can%20actually%20get%20a%20tentative%20cost%20of%20the%20house.%20Since%20very%20little%20manual%20labour%20is%20involved%2C%20most%20of%20the%20cost%20comes%20from%20the%20material.%20Hence%2C%20once%20the%20structure%20is%20ready%2C%20we%20take%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20customer%20and%20then%20finalise%20the%20deal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20the%20step%20of%20fabrication.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20factories%2C%20the%20steel%20frames%20are%20fabricated%20using%20advanced%20machinery.%20The%20sections%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20place%20and%20assembled%20there.%20If%20you%20look%20from%20outside%2C%20it%20would%20resemble%20a%20steel%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20structure%20is%20quite%20lightweight%20so%20it%20does%20not%20need%20any%20machinery%20to%20do%20the%20fit